Theory AOT_NaturalNumbers

1(*<*)
2theory AOT_NaturalNumbers
3  imports AOT_PossibleWorlds AOT_ExtendedRelationComprehension
4  abbrevs one-to-one = ‹⇩1⇩-⇩1›
5      and onto = ‹⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o›
6begin
7(*>*)
8
9section‹Natural Numbers›
10 
11AOT_define CorrelatesOneToOne :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ _›)
12  "1-1-cor": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ G ≡⇩d⇩f R↓ & F↓ & G↓ &
13                                   ∀x ([F]x → ∃!y([G]y & [R]xy)) &
14                                   ∀y ([G]y → ∃!x([F]x & [R]xy))›
15
16AOT_define MapsTo :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⟶ _›)
17  "fFG:1": ‹R |: F ⟶ G ≡⇩d⇩f R↓ & F↓ & G↓ & ∀x ([F]x → ∃!y([G]y & [R]xy))›
18
19AOT_define MapsToOneToOne :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶ _›)
20  "fFG:2": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶ G ≡⇩d⇩f
21      R |: F ⟶ G & ∀x∀y∀z (([F]x & [F]y & [G]z) → ([R]xz & [R]yz → x = y))›
22
23AOT_define MapsOnto :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o _›)
24  "fFG:3": ‹R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G ≡⇩d⇩f R |: F ⟶ G & ∀y ([G]y → ∃x([F]x & [R]xy))›
25
26AOT_define MapsOneToOneOnto :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o _›)
27  "fFG:4": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G ≡⇩d⇩f R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶ G & R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G›
28
29AOT_theorem "eq-1-1": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ G ≡ R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G›
30proof(rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
31  AOT_assume ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ G›
32  AOT_hence A: ‹∀x ([F]x → ∃!y([G]y & [R]xy))›
33        and B: ‹∀y ([G]y → ∃!x([F]x & [R]xy))›
34    using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "1-1-cor"] "&E" by blast+
35  AOT_have C: ‹R |: F ⟶ G›
36  proof (rule "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "fFG:1"]; rule "&I")
37    AOT_show ‹R↓ & F↓ & G↓›
38      using "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] "&I" by metis
39  next
40    AOT_show ‹∀x ([F]x → ∃!y([G]y & [R]xy))› by (rule A)
41  qed
42  AOT_show ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G›
43  proof (rule "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "fFG:4"]; rule "&I")
44    AOT_show ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶ G›
45    proof (rule "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "fFG:2"]; rule "&I")
46      AOT_show ‹R |: F ⟶ G› using C.
47    next
48      AOT_show ‹∀x∀y∀z ([F]x & [F]y & [G]z → ([R]xz & [R]yz → x = y))›
49      proof(rule GEN; rule GEN; rule GEN; rule "→I"; rule "→I")
50        fix x y z
51        AOT_assume 1: ‹[F]x & [F]y & [G]z›
52        moreover AOT_assume 2: ‹[R]xz & [R]yz›
53        ultimately AOT_have 3: ‹∃!x ([F]x & [R]xz)›
54          using B "&E" "∀E" "→E" by fast
55        AOT_show ‹x = y›
56          by (rule "uni-most"[THEN "→E", OF 3, THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=x],
57                              THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=y], THEN "→E"])
58             (metis "&I" "&E" 1 2)
59      qed
60    qed
61  next
62    AOT_show ‹R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G›
63    proof (rule "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "fFG:3"]; rule "&I")
64      AOT_show ‹R |: F ⟶ G› using C.
65    next
66      AOT_show ‹∀y ([G]y → ∃x ([F]x & [R]xy))›
67      proof(rule GEN; rule "→I")
68        fix y
69        AOT_assume ‹[G]y›
70        AOT_hence ‹∃!x ([F]x & [R]xy)›
71          using B[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
72        AOT_hence ‹∃x ([F]x & [R]xy & ∀β (([F]β & [R]βy) → β = x))›
73          using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
74        then AOT_obtain x where ‹[F]x & [R]xy›
75          using "∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
76        AOT_thus ‹∃x ([F]x & [R]xy)› by (rule "∃I")
77      qed
78    qed
79  qed
80next
81  AOT_assume ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G›
82  AOT_hence ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶ G› and ‹R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩o G›
83    using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "fFG:4"] "&E" by blast+
84  AOT_hence C: ‹R |: F ⟶ G›
85    and D: ‹∀x∀y∀z ([F]x & [F]y & [G]z → ([R]xz & [R]yz → x = y))›
86    and E: ‹∀y ([G]y → ∃x ([F]x & [R]xy))›
87    using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "fFG:2"] "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "fFG:3"] "&E" by blast+
88  AOT_show ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ G›
89  proof(rule "1-1-cor"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]; safe intro!: "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst])
90    AOT_show ‹∀x ([F]x → ∃!y ([G]y & [R]xy))›
91      using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "fFG:1", OF C] "&E" by blast
92  next
93    AOT_show ‹∀y ([G]y → ∃!x ([F]x & [R]xy))›
94    proof (rule "GEN"; rule "→I")
95      fix y
96      AOT_assume 0: ‹[G]y›
97      AOT_hence ‹∃x ([F]x & [R]xy)›
98        using E "∀E" "→E" by fast
99      then AOT_obtain a where a_prop: ‹[F]a & [R]ay›
100        using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
101      moreover AOT_have ‹∀z ([F]z & [R]zy → z = a)›
102      proof (rule GEN; rule "→I")
103        fix z
104        AOT_assume ‹[F]z & [R]zy›
105        AOT_thus ‹z = a›
106          using D[THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=z], THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=a],
107                  THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=y], THEN "→E", THEN "→E"]
108                a_prop 0 "&E" "&I" by metis
109      qed
110      ultimately AOT_have ‹∃x ([F]x & [R]xy & ∀z ([F]z & [R]zy → z = x))›
111        using "&I" "∃I"(2) by fast
112      AOT_thus ‹∃!x ([F]x & [R]xy)›
113        using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] by fast
114    qed
115  qed
116qed
117
118text‹We have already introduced the restricted type of Ordinary objects in the
119     Extended Relation Comprehension theory. However, make sure all variable names
120     are defined as expected (avoiding conflicts with situations
121     of possible world theory).›
122AOT_register_variable_names
123  Ordinary: u v r t s
124
125AOT_theorem "equi:1": ‹∃!u φ{u} ≡ ∃u (φ{u} & ∀v (φ{v} → v =⇩E u))›
126proof(rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
127  AOT_assume ‹∃!u φ{u}›
128  AOT_hence ‹∃!x (O!x & φ{x})›.
129  AOT_hence ‹∃x (O!x & φ{x} & ∀β (O!β & φ{β} → β = x))›
130    using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
131  then AOT_obtain x where x_prop: ‹O!x & φ{x} & ∀β (O!β & φ{β} → β = x)›
132    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
133  {
134    fix β
135    AOT_assume beta_ord: ‹O!β›
136    moreover AOT_assume ‹φ{β}›
137    ultimately AOT_have ‹β = x›
138      using x_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=β]] "&I" "→E" by blast
139    AOT_hence ‹β =⇩E x›
140      using "ord-=E=:1"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(1)[OF beta_ord],
141                        THEN "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"],
142                        THEN "≡E"(1)]
143      by blast
144  }
145  AOT_hence ‹(O!β → (φ{β} → β =⇩E x))› for β
146    using "→I" by blast
147  AOT_hence ‹∀β(O!β → (φ{β} → β =⇩E x))›
148    by (rule GEN)
149  AOT_hence ‹O!x & φ{x} & ∀y (O!y → (φ{y} → y =⇩E x))›
150    using x_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "&I" by blast
151  AOT_hence ‹O!x & (φ{x} & ∀y (O!y → (φ{y} → y =⇩E x)))›
152    using "&E" "&I" by meson
153  AOT_thus ‹∃u (φ{u} & ∀v (φ{v} → v =⇩E u))›
154    using "∃I" by fast
155next
156  AOT_assume ‹∃u (φ{u} & ∀v (φ{v} → v =⇩E u))›
157  AOT_hence ‹∃x (O!x & (φ{x} & ∀y (O!y → (φ{y} → y =⇩E x))))›
158    by blast
159  then AOT_obtain x where x_prop: ‹O!x & (φ{x} & ∀y (O!y → (φ{y} → y =⇩E x)))›
160    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
161  AOT_have ‹∀y ([O!]y & φ{y} → y = x)›
162  proof(rule GEN; rule "→I")
163    fix y
164    AOT_assume ‹O!y & φ{y}›
165    AOT_hence ‹y =⇩E x›
166      using x_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=y]]
167            "→E" "&E" by blast
168    AOT_thus ‹y = x›
169      using "ord-=E=:1"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(2)[OF x_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]],
170                        THEN "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"], THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
171  qed
172  AOT_hence ‹[O!]x & φ{x} & ∀y ([O!]y & φ{y} → y = x)›
173    using x_prop "&E" "&I" by meson
174  AOT_hence ‹∃x ([O!]x & φ{x} & ∀y ([O!]y & φ{y} → y = x))›
175    by (rule "∃I")
176  AOT_hence ‹∃!x (O!x & φ{x})›
177    by (rule "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
178  AOT_thus ‹∃!u φ{u}›.
179qed
180
181AOT_define CorrelatesEOneToOne :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹_ |: _ ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E _›)
182  "equi:2": ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G ≡⇩d⇩f R↓ & F↓ & G↓ &
183                               ∀u ([F]u → ∃!v([G]v & [R]uv)) &
184                               ∀v ([G]v → ∃!u([F]u & [R]uv))›
185
186AOT_define EquinumerousE :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (infixl "≈⇩E" 50)
187  "equi:3": ‹F ≈⇩E G ≡⇩d⇩f ∃R (R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G)›
188
189text‹Note: not explicitly in PLM.›
190AOT_theorem eq_den_1: ‹Π↓› if ‹Π ≈⇩E Π'›
191proof -
192  AOT_have ‹∃R (R |: Π ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E Π')›
193    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] that by blast
194  then AOT_obtain R where ‹R |: Π ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E Π'›
195    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
196  AOT_thus ‹Π↓›
197    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
198qed
199
200text‹Note: not explicitly in PLM.›
201AOT_theorem eq_den_2: ‹Π'↓› if ‹Π ≈⇩E Π'›
202proof -
203  AOT_have ‹∃R (R |: Π ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E Π')›
204    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] that by blast
205  then AOT_obtain R where ‹R |: Π ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E Π'›
206    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
207  AOT_thus ‹Π'↓›
208    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
209qed
210
211AOT_theorem "eq-part:1": ‹F ≈⇩E F›
212proof (safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]
213                    "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "equi:3"] "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "equi:2"] "∃I"(1))
214  fix x
215  AOT_assume 1: ‹O!x›
216  AOT_assume 2: ‹[F]x›
217  AOT_show ‹∃!v ([F]v & x =⇩E v)›
218  proof(rule "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)];
219        rule "∃I"(2)[where β=x];
220        safe dest!: "&E"(2)
221             intro!:  "&I" "→I" 1 2 Ordinary.GEN "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF 1])
222    AOT_show ‹v =⇩E x› if ‹x =⇩E v› for v
223      by (metis that "ord=Eequiv:2"[THEN "→E"])
224  qed
225next
226  fix y
227  AOT_assume 1: ‹O!y›
228  AOT_assume 2: ‹[F]y›
229  AOT_show ‹∃!u ([F]u & u =⇩E y)›
230    by(safe dest!: "&E"(2)
231            intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "∃I"(2)[where β=y]
232                    "&I" "→I" 1 2 GEN "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF 1])
233qed(auto simp: "=E[denotes]")
234
235
236AOT_theorem "eq-part:2": ‹F ≈⇩E G → G ≈⇩E F›
237proof (rule "→I")
238  AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E G›
239  AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
240    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
241  then AOT_obtain R where ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
242    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
243  AOT_hence 0: ‹R↓ & F↓ & G↓ & ∀u ([F]u → ∃!v([G]v & [R]uv)) &
244                            ∀v ([G]v → ∃!u([F]u & [R]uv))›
245    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
246
247  AOT_have ‹[λxy [R]yx]↓ & G↓ & F↓ & ∀u ([G]u → ∃!v([F]v & [λxy [R]yx]uv)) &
248                            ∀v ([F]v → ∃!u([G]u & [λxy [R]yx]uv))›
249  proof (AOT_subst ‹[λxy [R]yx]yx› ‹[R]xy› for: x y;
250        (safe intro!: "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] 0[THEN "&E"(2)]
251                      0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]; "cqt:2[lambda]")?)
252    AOT_modally_strict {
253      AOT_have ‹[λxy [R]yx]xy› if ‹[R]yx› for y x
254        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2"
255                 simp: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3" that)
256      moreover AOT_have ‹[R]yx› if ‹[λxy [R]yx]xy› for y x
257        using "β→C"(1)[where φ="λ(x,y). _ (x,y)" and κ⇩1κ⇩n="(_,_)",
258                        simplified, OF that, simplified].
259      ultimately AOT_show ‹[λxy [R]yx]αβ ≡ [R]βα› for α β
260        by (metis "deduction-theorem" "≡I")
261    }
262  qed
263  AOT_hence ‹[λxy [R]yx] |: G ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E F›
264    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] by blast
265  AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: G ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E F›
266    by (rule "∃I"(1)) "cqt:2[lambda]"
267  AOT_thus ‹G ≈⇩E F›
268    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] by blast
269qed
270
271text‹Note: not explicitly in PLM.›
272AOT_theorem "eq-part:2[terms]": ‹Π ≈⇩E Π' → Π' ≈⇩E Π›
273  using "eq-part:2"[unvarify F G] eq_den_1 eq_den_2 "→I" by meson
274declare "eq-part:2[terms]"[THEN "→E", sym]
275
276AOT_theorem "eq-part:3": ‹(F ≈⇩E G & G ≈⇩E H) → F ≈⇩E H›
277proof (rule "→I")
278  AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E G & G ≈⇩E H›
279  then AOT_obtain R⇩1 and R⇩2 where
280       ‹R⇩1 |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
281   and ‹R⇩2 |: G ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E H›
282    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by metis
283  AOT_hence θ: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v([G]v & [R⇩1]uv)) & ∀v ([G]v → ∃!u([F]u & [R⇩1]uv))›
284        and ξ: ‹∀u ([G]u → ∃!v([H]v & [R⇩2]uv)) & ∀v ([H]v → ∃!u([G]u & [R⇩2]uv))›
285    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)]
286          "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]
287          "&I" by blast+
288  AOT_have ‹∃R R = [λxy O!x & O!y & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]xv & [R⇩2]vy)]›
289    by (rule "free-thms:3[lambda]") cqt_2_lambda_inst_prover
290  then AOT_obtain R where R_def: ‹R = [λxy O!x & O!y & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]xv & [R⇩2]vy)]›
291    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
292  AOT_have 1: ‹∃!v (([H]v & [R]uv))› if a: ‹[O!]u› and b: ‹[F]u› for u
293  proof (rule "≡E"(2)[OF "equi:1"])
294    AOT_obtain b where
295      b_prop: ‹[O!]b & ([G]b & [R⇩1]ub & ∀v ([G]v & [R⇩1]uv → v =⇩E b))›
296      using θ[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E",
297              OF a b, THEN "≡E"(1)[OF "equi:1"]]
298            "∃E"[rotated] by blast
299    AOT_obtain c where
300      c_prop: "[O!]c & ([H]c & [R⇩2]bc & ∀v ([H]v & [R⇩2]bv → v =⇩E c))"
301      using ξ[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=b], THEN "→E",
302              OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)], THEN "→E",
303              OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)],
304              THEN "≡E"(1)[OF "equi:1"]]
305    "∃E"[rotated] by blast
306    AOT_show ‹∃v ([H]v & [R]uv & ∀v' ([H]v' & [R]uv' → v' =⇩E v))›
307    proof (safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" "∃I"(2)[where β=c])
308      AOT_show ‹O!c› using c_prop "&E" by blast
309    next
310      AOT_show ‹[H]c› using c_prop "&E" by blast
311    next
312      AOT_have 0: ‹[O!]u & [O!]c & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]uv & [R⇩2]vc)›
313        by (safe intro!: "&I" a c_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "∃I"(2)[where β=b]
314                         b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1)]
315                         c_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)])
316      AOT_show ‹[R]uc›
317        by (auto intro: "rule=E"[rotated, OF R_def[symmetric]]
318                 intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2"
319                 simp: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3" 0)
320    next
321      fix x
322      AOT_assume ordx: ‹O!x›
323      AOT_assume ‹[H]x & [R]ux›
324      AOT_hence hx: ‹[H]x› and ‹[R]ux› using "&E" by blast+
325      AOT_hence ‹[λxy O!x & O!y & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]xv & [R⇩2]vy)]ux›
326        using "rule=E"[rotated, OF R_def] by fast
327      AOT_hence ‹O!u & O!x & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]uv & [R⇩2]vx)›
328        by (rule "β→C"(1)[where φ="λ(κ,κ'). _ κ κ'" and κ⇩1κ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified])
329      then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹O!z & ([G]z & [R⇩1]uz & [R⇩2]zx)›
330        using "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
331      AOT_hence ‹z =⇩E b›
332        using b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=z]]
333        using "&E" "→E" by metis
334      AOT_hence ‹z = b›
335        by (metis "=E-simple:2"[THEN "→E"])
336      AOT_hence ‹[R⇩2]bx›
337        using z_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2)] "rule=E" by fast
338      AOT_thus ‹x =⇩E c›
339        using c_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=x],
340                     THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF ordx]
341              hx "&I" by blast
342    qed
343  qed
344  AOT_have 2: ‹∃!u (([F]u & [R]uv))› if a: ‹[O!]v› and b: ‹[H]v› for v
345  proof (rule "≡E"(2)[OF "equi:1"])
346    AOT_obtain b where
347      b_prop: ‹[O!]b & ([G]b & [R⇩2]bv & ∀u ([G]u & [R⇩2]uv → u =⇩E b))›
348      using ξ[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E",
349              OF a b, THEN "≡E"(1)[OF "equi:1"]]
350            "∃E"[rotated] by blast
351    AOT_obtain c where
352      c_prop: "[O!]c & ([F]c & [R⇩1]cb & ∀v ([F]v & [R⇩1]vb → v =⇩E c))"
353      using θ[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=b], THEN "→E",
354              OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)], THEN "→E",
355              OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)],
356              THEN "≡E"(1)[OF "equi:1"]]
357    "∃E"[rotated] by blast
358    AOT_show ‹∃u ([F]u & [R]uv & ∀v' ([F]v' & [R]v'v → v' =⇩E u))›
359    proof (safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" "∃I"(2)[where β=c])
360      AOT_show ‹O!c› using c_prop "&E" by blast
361    next
362      AOT_show ‹[F]c› using c_prop "&E" by blast
363    next
364      AOT_have ‹[O!]c & [O!]v & ∃u ([G]u & [R⇩1]cu & [R⇩2]uv)›
365        by (safe intro!: "&I" a "∃I"(2)[where β=b] 
366                     c_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]
367                     b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
368                     b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]
369                     c_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)])
370      AOT_thus ‹[R]cv›
371        by (auto intro: "rule=E"[rotated, OF R_def[symmetric]]
372                 intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2"
373                 simp: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")
374    next
375      fix x
376      AOT_assume ordx: ‹O!x›
377      AOT_assume ‹[F]x & [R]xv›
378      AOT_hence hx: ‹[F]x› and ‹[R]xv› using "&E" by blast+
379      AOT_hence ‹[λxy O!x & O!y & ∃v ([G]v & [R⇩1]xv & [R⇩2]vy)]xv›
380        using "rule=E"[rotated, OF R_def] by fast
381      AOT_hence ‹O!x & O!v & ∃u ([G]u & [R⇩1]xu & [R⇩2]uv)›
382        by (rule "β→C"(1)[where φ="λ(κ,κ'). _ κ κ'" and κ⇩1κ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified])
383      then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹O!z & ([G]z & [R⇩1]xz & [R⇩2]zv)›
384        using "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
385      AOT_hence ‹z =⇩E b›
386        using b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=z]]
387        using "&E" "→E" "&I" by metis
388      AOT_hence ‹z = b›
389        by (metis "=E-simple:2"[THEN "→E"])
390      AOT_hence ‹[R⇩1]xb›
391        using z_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)] "rule=E" by fast
392      AOT_thus ‹x =⇩E c›
393        using c_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=x],
394                     THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF ordx]
395              hx "&I" by blast
396    qed
397  qed
398  AOT_show ‹F ≈⇩E H›
399    apply (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
400    apply (rule "∃I"(2)[where β=R])
401    by (auto intro!: 1 2 "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]
402                     Ordinary.GEN "→I" Ordinary.ψ)
403qed

405text‹Note: not explicitly in PLM.›
406AOT_theorem "eq-part:3[terms]": ‹Π ≈⇩E Π''› if ‹Π ≈⇩E Π'› and ‹Π' ≈⇩E Π''›
407  using "eq-part:3"[unvarify F G H, THEN "→E"] eq_den_1 eq_den_2 "→I" "&I"
408  by (metis that(1) that(2))
409declare "eq-part:3[terms]"[trans]
410
411AOT_theorem "eq-part:4": ‹F ≈⇩E G ≡ ∀H (H ≈⇩E F ≡ H ≈⇩E G)›
412proof(rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
413  AOT_assume 0: ‹F ≈⇩E G›
414  AOT_hence 1: ‹G ≈⇩E F› using "eq-part:2"[THEN "→E"] by blast
415  AOT_show ‹∀H (H ≈⇩E F ≡ H ≈⇩E G)›
416  proof (rule GEN; rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
417    AOT_show ‹H ≈⇩E G› if ‹H ≈⇩E F› for H using 0
418      by (meson "&I" "eq-part:3" that "vdash-properties:6")
419  next
420    AOT_show ‹H ≈⇩E F› if ‹H ≈⇩E G› for H using 1
421      by (metis "&I" "eq-part:3" that "vdash-properties:6")
422  qed
423next
424  AOT_assume ‹∀H (H ≈⇩E F ≡ H ≈⇩E G)›
425  AOT_hence ‹F ≈⇩E F ≡ F ≈⇩E G› using "∀E" by blast
426  AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E G› using "eq-part:1" "≡E" by blast
427qed

429AOT_define MapsE :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› ("_ |: _ ⟶E _")
430  "equi-rem:1":
431  ‹R |: F ⟶E G ≡⇩d⇩f R↓ & F↓ & G↓ & ∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))›
432
433AOT_define MapsEOneToOne :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› ("_ |: _ ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E _")
434  "equi-rem:2":
435  ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E G ≡⇩d⇩f
436      R |: F ⟶E G & ∀t∀u∀v (([F]t & [F]u & [G]v) → ([R]tv & [R]uv → t =⇩E u))›
437
438AOT_define MapsEOnto :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› ("_ |: _ ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE _")
439  "equi-rem:3":
440  ‹R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G ≡⇩d⇩f R |: F ⟶E G & ∀v ([G]v → ∃u ([F]u & [R]uv))›
441
442AOT_define MapsEOneToOneOnto :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› ("_ |: _ ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE _")
443  "equi-rem:4":
444  ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G ≡⇩d⇩f R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E G & R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
445
446AOT_theorem "equi-rem-thm":
447  ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G ≡ R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
448proof -
449  AOT_have ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G ≡ R |: [λx O!x & [F]x] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ [λx O!x & [G]x]›
450  proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" "&I")
451    AOT_assume ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
452    AOT_hence ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))›
453          and ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))›
454      using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
455    AOT_hence a: ‹([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))›
456          and b: ‹([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))› for u v
457      using "Ordinary.∀E" by fast+
458    AOT_have ‹([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x → ∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]xy))› for x
459      apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]x› ‹[O!]x & [F]x›)
460       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
461       apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
462      apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]x› ‹[O!]x & [G]x› for: x)
463       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
464       apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
465      apply (AOT_subst ‹O!y & [G]y & [R]xy› ‹O!y & ([G]y & [R]xy)› for: y)
466       apply (meson "≡E"(6) "Associativity of &" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
467      apply (rule "→I") apply (frule "&E"(1)) apply (drule "&E"(2))
468      by (fact a[unconstrain u, THEN "→E", THEN "→E", of x])
469    AOT_hence A: ‹∀x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x → ∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]xy))›
470      by (rule GEN)
471    AOT_have ‹([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y → ∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xy))› for y
472      apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]y› ‹[O!]y & [G]y›)
473       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
474       apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
475      apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]x› ‹[O!]x & [F]x› for: x)
476       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
477       apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
478      apply (AOT_subst ‹O!x & [F]x & [R]xy› ‹O!x & ([F]x & [R]xy)› for: x)
479       apply (meson "≡E"(6) "Associativity of &" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
480      apply (rule "→I") apply (frule "&E"(1)) apply (drule "&E"(2))
481      by (fact b[unconstrain v, THEN "→E", THEN "→E", of y])
482    AOT_hence B: ‹∀y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y → ∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xy))›
483      by (rule GEN)
484    AOT_show ‹R |: [λx [O!]x & [F]x] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ [λx [O!]x & [G]x]›
485      by (safe intro!: "1-1-cor"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I"
486                       "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] A B)
487          "cqt:2[lambda]"+
488  next
489    AOT_assume ‹R |: [λx [O!]x & [F]x] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ [λx [O!]x & [G]x]›
490    AOT_hence a: ‹([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x → ∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]xy))› and 
491              b: ‹([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y → ∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xy))› for x y
492      using "1-1-cor"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" "∀E"(2) by blast+
493    AOT_have ‹[F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv)› for u
494    proof (safe intro!: "→I")
495      AOT_assume fu: ‹[F]u›
496      AOT_have 0: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]u›
497        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]
498                         Ordinary.ψ fu "&I")
499      AOT_show ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv)›
500        apply (AOT_subst ‹[O!]x & ([G]x & [R]ux)›
501                         ‹([O!]x & [G]x) & [R]ux› for: x)
502         apply (simp add: "Associativity of &")
503        apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[O!]x & [G]x›
504                                   ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]x› for: x)
505         apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
506         apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
507        using a[THEN "→E", OF 0] by blast
508    qed
509    AOT_hence A: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))›
510      by (rule Ordinary.GEN)
511    AOT_have ‹[G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv)› for v
512    proof (safe intro!: "→I")
513      AOT_assume gu: ‹[G]v›
514      AOT_have 0: ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]v›
515        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]
516                         Ordinary.ψ gu "&I")
517      AOT_show ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv)›
518        apply (AOT_subst ‹[O!]x & ([F]x & [R]xv)› ‹([O!]x & [F]x) & [R]xv› for: x)
519         apply (simp add: "Associativity of &")
520        apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[O!]x & [F]x›‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]x›  for: x)
521         apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
522         apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
523        using b[THEN "→E", OF 0] by blast
524    qed
525    AOT_hence B: ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))› by (rule Ordinary.GEN)
526    AOT_show ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
527      by (safe intro!: "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" A B "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst])
528  qed
529  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
530  proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" "&I")
531    AOT_assume ‹R |: [λx [O!]x & [F]x] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ [λx [O!]x & [G]x]›
532    AOT_hence a: ‹([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x → ∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]xy))› and 
533              b: ‹([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y → ∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xy))› for x y
534      using "1-1-cor"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" "∀E"(2) by blast+
535    AOT_show ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
536    proof (safe intro!: "equi-rem:4"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "equi-rem:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]
537                        "equi-rem:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "equi-rem:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]
538                        "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.GEN "→I")
539      fix u
540      AOT_assume fu: ‹[F]u›
541      AOT_have 0: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]u›
542        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]
543                         Ordinary.ψ fu "&I")
544      AOT_hence 1: ‹∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]uy)›
545        using a[THEN "→E"] by blast
546      AOT_show ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv)›
547        apply (AOT_subst ‹[O!]x & ([G]x & [R]ux)› ‹([O!]x & [G]x) & [R]ux› for: x)
548         apply (simp add: "Associativity of &")
549        apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[O!]x & [G]x› ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]x› for: x)
550         apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
551         apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
552        by (fact 1)
553    next
554      fix t u v
555      AOT_assume ‹[F]t & [F]u & [G]v› and rtv_tuv: ‹[R]tv & [R]uv›
556      AOT_hence oft: ‹[λx O!x & [F]x]t› and
557                ofu: ‹[λx O!x & [F]x]u› and
558                ogv: ‹[λx O!x & [G]x]v›
559        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I"
560                 simp: Ordinary.ψ dest: "&E")
561      AOT_hence ‹∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xv)›
562        using b[THEN "→E"] by blast
563      then AOT_obtain a where
564          a_prop: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]a & [R]av &
565                   ∀x (([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xv) → x = a)›
566        using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "∃E"[rotated] by blast
567      AOT_hence ua: ‹u = a›
568        using ofu rtv_tuv[THEN "&E"(2)] "∀E"(2) "→E" "&I" "&E"(2) by blast
569      moreover AOT_have ta: ‹t = a›
570        using a_prop oft rtv_tuv[THEN "&E"(1)] "∀E"(2) "→E" "&I" "&E"(2) by blast
571      ultimately AOT_have ‹t = u› by (metis "rule=E" id_sym)
572      AOT_thus ‹t =⇩E u›
573        using "rule=E" id_sym "ord=Eequiv:1" Ordinary.ψ ta ua "→E" by fast
574    next
575      fix u
576      AOT_assume ‹[F]u›
577      AOT_hence ‹[λx O!x & [F]x]u›
578        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I"
579                 simp: "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]  Ordinary.ψ)
580      AOT_hence ‹∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]uy)›
581        using a[THEN "→E"] by blast
582      then AOT_obtain a where
583        a_prop: ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]a & [R]ua &
584                 ∀x (([λx [O!]x & [G]x]x & [R]ux) → x = a)›
585        using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "∃E"[rotated] by blast
586      AOT_have ‹O!a & [G]a›
587        by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)])
588      AOT_hence ‹O!a› and ‹[G]a› using "&E" by blast+
589      moreover AOT_have ‹∀v ([G]v & [R]uv → v =⇩E a)›
590      proof(safe intro!: Ordinary.GEN "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
591        fix v
592        AOT_assume ‹[G]v› and ruv: ‹[R]uv›
593        AOT_hence ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]v›
594          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" simp: Ordinary.ψ)
595        AOT_hence ‹v = a›
596          using a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", OF "&I"] ruv by blast
597        AOT_thus ‹v =⇩E a›
598          using "rule=E" "ord=Eequiv:1" Ordinary.ψ "→E" by fast
599      qed
600      ultimately AOT_have ‹O!a & ([G]a & [R]ua & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R]uv' → v' =⇩E a))›
601        using "∃I" "&I" a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)] by simp
602      AOT_hence ‹∃v ([G]v & [R]uv & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R]uv' → v' =⇩E v))›
603        by (rule "∃I")
604      AOT_thus ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv)›
605        by (rule "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
606    next
607      fix v
608      AOT_assume ‹[G]v›
609      AOT_hence ‹[λx O!x & [G]x]v›
610        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" Ordinary.ψ)
611      AOT_hence ‹∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xv)›
612        using b[THEN "→E"] by blast
613      then AOT_obtain a where
614        a_prop: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]a & [R]av &
615                 ∀y ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]y & [R]yv → y = a)›
616        using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "∃E"[rotated]] by blast
617      AOT_have ‹O!a & [F]a›
618        by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)])
619      AOT_hence ‹O!a & ([F]a & [R]av)›
620        using a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)] "&E" "&I" by metis
621      AOT_thus ‹∃u ([F]u & [R]uv)›
622        by (rule "∃I")
623    qed
624  next
625    AOT_assume ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
626    AOT_hence 1: ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E G›
627          and 2: ‹R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
628      using "equi-rem:4"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
629    AOT_hence 3: ‹R |: F ⟶E G›
630          and A: ‹∀t ∀u ∀v ([F]t & [F]u & [G]v → ([R]tv & [R]uv → t =⇩E u))›
631      using "equi-rem:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", OF 1] "&E" by blast+
632    AOT_hence B: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))›
633      using "equi-rem:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
634    AOT_have C: ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃u ([F]u & [R]uv))›
635      using "equi-rem:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", OF 2] "&E" by blast
636    AOT_show ‹R |: [λx [O!]x & [F]x] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷ [λx [O!]x & [G]x]›
637    proof (rule "1-1-cor"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"];
638           safe intro!: "&I" "cqt:2" GEN "→I")
639      fix x
640      AOT_assume 1: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]x›
641      AOT_have ‹O!x & [F]x›
642        by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: 1)
643      AOT_hence ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]xv)›
644        using B[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E"] "&E" by blast
645      then AOT_obtain y where
646        y_prop: ‹O!y & ([G]y & [R]xy & ∀u ([G]u & [R]xu → u =⇩E y))›
647        using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] "∃E"[rotated] by fastforce
648      AOT_hence ‹[λx O!x & [G]x]y›
649        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" dest: "&E")
650      moreover AOT_have ‹∀z ([λx O!x & [G]x]z & [R]xz → z = y)›
651      proof(safe intro!: GEN "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
652        fix z
653        AOT_assume 1: ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]z›
654        AOT_have 2: ‹O!z & [G]z›
655          by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: 1)
656        moreover AOT_assume ‹[R]xz›
657        ultimately AOT_have ‹z =⇩E y›
658          using y_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2),
659                       THEN "→E", THEN "→E", rotated, OF "&I"] "&E"
660          by blast
661        AOT_thus ‹z = y›
662          using 2[THEN "&E"(1)] by (metis "=E-simple:2" "→E")
663      qed
664      ultimately AOT_have ‹[λx O!x & [G]x]y & [R]xy &
665                           ∀z ([λx O!x & [G]x]z & [R]xz → z = y)›
666        using y_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)] "&I" by auto
667      AOT_hence ‹∃y ([λx O!x & [G]x]y & [R]xy &
668                    ∀z ([λx O!x & [G]x]z & [R]xz → z = y))›
669        by (rule "∃I")
670      AOT_thus ‹∃!y ([λx [O!]x & [G]x]y & [R]xy)›
671        using "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] by fast
672    next
673      fix y
674      AOT_assume 1: ‹[λx [O!]x & [G]x]y›
675      AOT_have oy_gy: ‹O!y & [G]y›
676        by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: 1)
677      AOT_hence ‹∃u ([F]u & [R]uy)›
678        using C[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", THEN "→E"] "&E" by blast
679      then AOT_obtain x where x_prop: ‹O!x & ([F]x & [R]xy)›
680        using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
681      AOT_hence ofx: ‹[λx O!x & [F]x]x›
682        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" dest: "&E")
683      AOT_have ‹∃α ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]α & [R]αy &
684                    ∀β ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]β & [R]βy → β = α))›
685      proof (safe intro!: "∃I"(2)[where β=x] "&I" GEN "→I")
686        AOT_show ‹[λx O!x & [F]x]x› using ofx.
687      next
688        AOT_show ‹[R]xy› using x_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2)].
689      next
690        fix z
691        AOT_assume 1: ‹[λx [O!]x & [F]x]z & [R]zy›
692        AOT_have oz_fz: ‹O!z & [F]z›
693          by (rule "β→C"(1)) (auto simp: 1[THEN "&E"(1)])
694        AOT_have ‹z =⇩E x›
695          using A[THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=z], THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=x],
696                  THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=y], THEN "→E",
697                  THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF oz_fz[THEN "&E"(1)],
698                  OF x_prop[THEN "&E"(1)], OF oy_gy[THEN "&E"(1)], OF "&I", OF "&I",
699                  OF oz_fz[THEN "&E"(2)], OF x_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1)],
700                  OF oy_gy[THEN "&E"(2)], OF "&I", OF 1[THEN "&E"(2)],
701                  OF x_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2)]].
702        AOT_thus ‹z = x›
703          by (metis "=E-simple:2" "vdash-properties:10")
704      qed
705      AOT_thus ‹∃!x ([λx [O!]x & [F]x]x & [R]xy)›
706        by (rule "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
707    qed
708  qed
709  finally show ?thesis.
710qed
711
712AOT_theorem "empty-approx:1": ‹(¬∃u [F]u & ¬∃v [H]v) → F ≈⇩E H›
713proof(rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
714  AOT_assume 0: ‹¬∃u [F]u› and 1: ‹¬∃v [H]v›
715  AOT_have ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([H]v & [R]uv))› for R
716  proof(rule Ordinary.GEN; rule "→I"; rule "raa-cor:1")
717    fix u
718    AOT_assume ‹[F]u›
719    AOT_hence ‹∃u [F]u› using "Ordinary.∃I" "&I" by fast
720    AOT_thus ‹∃u [F]u & ¬∃u [F]u› using "&I" 0 by blast
721  qed
722  moreover AOT_have ‹∀v ([H]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))› for R
723  proof(rule Ordinary.GEN; rule "→I"; rule "raa-cor:1")
724    fix v
725    AOT_assume ‹[H]v›
726    AOT_hence ‹∃v [H]v› using "Ordinary.∃I" "&I" by fast
727    AOT_thus ‹∃v [H]v & ¬∃v [H]v› using 1 "&I" by blast
728  qed
729  ultimately AOT_have ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E H› for R
730    apply (safe intro!: "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" GEN "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst])
731    using "∀E" by blast+
732  AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E H› by (rule "∃I")
733  AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E H›
734    by (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
735qed
736
737AOT_theorem "empty-approx:2": ‹(∃u [F]u & ¬∃v [H]v) → ¬(F ≈⇩E H)›
738proof(rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2); rule "raa-cor:2")
739  AOT_assume 1: ‹∃u [F]u› and 2: ‹¬∃v [H]v›
740  AOT_obtain b where b_prop: ‹O!b & [F]b›
741    using 1 "∃E"[rotated] by blast
742  AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E H›
743  AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E H›
744    by (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"])
745  then AOT_obtain R where ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E H›
746    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
747  AOT_hence θ: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([H]v & [R]uv))›
748    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
749  AOT_have ‹∃!v ([H]v & [R]bv)› for u
750    using θ[THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=b], THEN "→E", THEN "→E",
751            OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)], OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]].
752  AOT_hence ‹∃v ([H]v & [R]bv & ∀u ([H]u & [R]bu → u =⇩E v))›
753    by (rule "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)])
754  then AOT_obtain x where ‹O!x & ([H]x & [R]bx & ∀u ([H]u & [R]bu → u =⇩E x))›
755    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
756  AOT_hence ‹O!x & [H]x› using "&E" "&I" by blast
757  AOT_hence ‹∃v [H]v› by (rule "∃I")
758  AOT_thus ‹∃v [H]v & ¬∃v [H]v› using 2 "&I" by blast
759qed

762AOT_define FminusU :: ‹Π ⇒ τ ⇒ Π› ("_⇧-⇧_")
763  "F-u": ‹[F]⇧-⇧x =⇩d⇩f [λz [F]z & z ≠⇩E x]›
764
765text‹Note: not explicitly in PLM.›
766AOT_theorem "F-u[den]": ‹[F]⇧-⇧x↓›
767  by (rule "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)[OF "F-u", where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
768
769AOT_theorem eqP': ‹F ≈⇩E G & [F]u & [G]v → [F]⇧-⇧u ≈⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v›
770proof (rule "→I"; frule "&E"(2); drule "&E"(1); frule "&E"(2); drule "&E"(1))
771  AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E G›
772  AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
773    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
774  then AOT_obtain R where R_prop: ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
775    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
776  AOT_hence A: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))›
777        and B: ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))›
778    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
779  AOT_have ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
780    using "equi-rem-thm"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF R_prop].
781  AOT_hence ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E G & R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
782    using "equi-rem:4"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
783  AOT_hence C: ‹∀t∀u∀v (([F]t & [F]u & [G]v) → ([R]tv & [R]uv → t =⇩E u))›
784    using "equi-rem:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
785  AOT_assume fu: ‹[F]u›
786  AOT_assume gv: ‹[G]v›
787  AOT_have ‹[λz [Π]z & z ≠⇩E κ]↓› for Π κ
788    by "cqt:2[lambda]"
789  note Π_minus_κI = "rule-id-df:2:b[2]"[
790      where τ=‹(λ(Π, κ). «[Π]⇧-⇧κ»)›, simplified, OF "F-u", simplified, OF this]
791   and Π_minus_κE = "rule-id-df:2:a[2]"[
792      where τ=‹(λ(Π, κ). «[Π]⇧-⇧κ»)›, simplified, OF "F-u", simplified, OF this]
793  AOT_have Π_minus_κ_den: ‹[Π]⇧-⇧κ↓› for Π κ
794    by (rule Π_minus_κI) "cqt:2[lambda]"+
795  {
796    fix R
797    AOT_assume R_prop: ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
798    AOT_hence A: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))›
799          and B: ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))›
800      using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
801    AOT_have ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
802      using "equi-rem-thm"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF R_prop].
803    AOT_hence ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E G & R |: F ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE G›
804      using "equi-rem:4"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
805    AOT_hence C: ‹∀t∀u∀v (([F]t & [F]u & [G]v) → ([R]tv & [R]uv → t =⇩E u))›
806      using "equi-rem:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
807
808    AOT_assume Ruv: ‹[R]uv›
809    AOT_have ‹R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v›
810    proof(safe intro!: "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst]
811                       Π_minus_κ_den Ordinary.GEN "→I")
812      fix u'
813      AOT_assume ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]u'›
814      AOT_hence 0: ‹[λz [F]z & z ≠⇩E u]u'›
815        using Π_minus_κE by fast
816      AOT_have 0: ‹[F]u' & u' ≠⇩E u›
817        by (rule "β→C"(1)[where κ⇩1κ⇩n="AOT_term_of_var (Ordinary.Rep u')"]) (fact 0)
818      AOT_have ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]u'v)›
819        using A[THEN "Ordinary.∀E"[where α=u'], THEN "→E", OF 0[THEN "&E"(1)]].
820      then AOT_obtain v' where
821        v'_prop: ‹[G]v' & [R]u'v' & ∀ t ([G]t & [R]u't → t =⇩E v')›
822        using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by fastforce
823
824      AOT_show ‹∃!v' ([[G]⇧-⇧v]v' & [R]u'v')›
825      proof (safe intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=v']
826                          "&I" Ordinary.GEN "→I")
827        AOT_show ‹[[G]⇧-⇧v]v'›
828        proof (rule Π_minus_κI; 
829               safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" "thm-neg=E"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
830          AOT_show ‹[G]v'› using v'_prop "&E" by blast
831        next
832          AOT_show ‹¬v' =⇩E v›
833          proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
834            AOT_assume ‹v' =⇩E v›
835            AOT_hence ‹v' = v› by (metis "=E-simple:2" "→E")
836            AOT_hence Ruv': ‹[R]uv'› using "rule=E" Ruv id_sym by fast
837            AOT_have ‹u' =⇩E u›
838              by (rule C[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "Ordinary.∀E",
839                         THEN "Ordinary.∀E"[where α=v'], THEN "→E", THEN "→E"])
840                 (safe intro!: "&I" 0[THEN "&E"(1)] fu
841                               v'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
842                               Ruv' v'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)])
843            moreover AOT_have ‹¬(u' =⇩E u)›
844              using "0" "&E"(2) "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E" by blast
845            ultimately AOT_show ‹u' =⇩E u & ¬u' =⇩E u› using "&I" by blast
846          qed
847        qed
848      next
849        AOT_show ‹[R]u'v'› using v'_prop "&E" by blast
850      next
851        fix t
852        AOT_assume t_prop: ‹[[G]⇧-⇧v]t & [R]u't›
853        AOT_have gt_t_noteq_v: ‹[G]t & t ≠⇩E v›
854          apply (rule "β→C"(1)[where κ⇩1κ⇩n="AOT_term_of_var (Ordinary.Rep t)"])
855          apply (rule Π_minus_κE)
856          by (fact t_prop[THEN "&E"(1)])
857        AOT_show ‹t =⇩E v'›
858          using v'_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E",
859                        OF "&I", OF gt_t_noteq_v[THEN "&E"(1)],
860                        OF t_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]].
861      qed
862    next
863      fix v'
864      AOT_assume G_minus_v_v': ‹[[G]⇧-⇧v]v'›
865      AOT_have gt_t_noteq_v: ‹[G]v' & v' ≠⇩E v›
866        apply (rule "β→C"(1)[where κ⇩1κ⇩n="AOT_term_of_var (Ordinary.Rep v')"])
867        apply (rule Π_minus_κE)
868        by (fact G_minus_v_v')
869      AOT_have ‹∃!u([F]u & [R]uv')›
870        using B[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E", OF gt_t_noteq_v[THEN "&E"(1)]].
871      then AOT_obtain u' where
872        u'_prop: ‹[F]u' & [R]u'v' & ∀t ([F]t & [R]tv' → t =⇩E u')›
873        using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by fastforce
874      AOT_show ‹∃!u' ([[F]⇧-⇧u]u' & [R]u'v')›
875      proof (safe intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=u'] "&I"
876                          u'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)] Ordinary.GEN "→I")
877        AOT_show ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]u'›
878        proof (rule Π_minus_κI;
879               safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" "thm-neg=E"[THEN "≡E"(2)]
880               u'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]; rule "raa-cor:2")
881          AOT_assume u'_eq_u: ‹u' =⇩E u›
882          AOT_hence ‹u' = u›
883            using "=E-simple:2" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
884          AOT_hence Ru'v: ‹[R]u'v› using "rule=E" Ruv id_sym by fast
885          AOT_have ‹v' ≠⇩E v›
886            using "&E"(2) gt_t_noteq_v by blast
887          AOT_hence v'_noteq_v: ‹¬(v' =⇩E v)› by (metis "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E")
888          AOT_have ‹∃u ([G]u & [R]u'u & ∀v ([G]v & [R]u'v → v =⇩E u))›
889            using A[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E",
890                    OF u'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)],
891                    THEN "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)]].
892          then AOT_obtain t where
893            t_prop: ‹[G]t & [R]u't & ∀v ([G]v & [R]u'v → v =⇩E t)›
894            using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by meson
895          AOT_have ‹v =⇩E t› if ‹[G]v› and ‹[R]u'v› for v
896            using t_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E",
897                         OF "&I", OF that].
898          AOT_hence ‹v' =⇩E t› and ‹v =⇩E t›
899            by (auto simp: gt_t_noteq_v[THEN "&E"(1)] Ru'v gv
900                           u'_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)])
901          AOT_hence ‹v' =⇩E v›
902            using "rule=E" "=E-simple:2" id_sym "→E" by fast
903          AOT_thus ‹v' =⇩E v & ¬v' =⇩E v›
904            using v'_noteq_v "&I" by blast
905        qed
906      next
907        fix t

1227               (safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" prod_denotesI Ordinary.ψ
1228                             "∨I"(2) 0 "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E"])
1229        next
1230          fix u'
1231          AOT_assume ‹[F]u' & [R⇩1]u'v'›
1232          AOT_hence 0: ‹[R⇩1]u'v›
1233            using "rule=E"[rotated, OF u'_eq_u] "&E"(2) by fast
1234          AOT_have 1: ‹[«?R»]u'v›
1235            by (rule "rule=E"[rotated, OF R⇩1_def]) (fact 0)
1236          AOT_have 2: ‹(u' ≠⇩E u & v ≠⇩E v & [R]u'v) ∨
1237                       (u' =⇩E a & v =⇩E b) ∨
1238                       (u' =⇩E u & v =⇩E v)›
1239            using "β→C"(1)[OF 1, simplified] by simp
1240          AOT_have ‹¬v ≠⇩E v›
1241            using "≡E"(4) "modus-tollens:1" "ord=Eequiv:1" Ordinary.ψ
1242                  "reductio-aa:2" "thm-neg=E" by blast
1243          AOT_hence ‹¬((u' ≠⇩E u & v ≠⇩E v & [R]u'v) ∨ (u' =⇩E a & v =⇩E b))›
1244            by (metis "&E"(1) "&E"(2) "∨E"(3) not_v_eq_b "raa-cor:3")
1245          AOT_hence ‹(u' =⇩E u & v =⇩E v)›
1246            using 2 by (metis "∨E"(2))
1247          AOT_thus ‹u' =⇩E u›
1248            using "&E" by blast
1249        qed
1250      }
1251      moreover {
1252        AOT_assume 0: ‹v' =⇩E b›
1253        AOT_hence v'_eq_b: ‹v' = b›
1254          using "=E-simple:2" "→E" by blast
1255        AOT_have ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R⇩1]uv')›
1256        proof (safe intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "∃I"(2)[where β=a] "&I"
1257                            Ordinary.GEN "→I" b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] Oa fa
1258                            b_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)])
1259          AOT_show ‹[R⇩1]av'›
1260            apply (rule "rule=E"[rotated, OF R⇩1_def[symmetric]])
1261            apply (safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" prod_denotesI)
1262            apply (rule "∨I"(1); rule "∨I"(2); rule "&I")
1263            using Oa "ord=Eequiv:1" "→E" apply blast
1264            using "0" by blast
1265        next
1266          fix u'
1267          AOT_assume fu'_R1u'v': ‹[F]u' & [R⇩1]u'v'›
1268          AOT_hence 0: ‹[R⇩1]u'b›
1269            using v'_eq_b by (meson "rule=E" "&E"(2))
1270          AOT_have 1: ‹[«?R»]u'b›
1271            by (rule "rule=E"[rotated, OF R⇩1_def]) (fact 0)
1272          AOT_have ‹(u' ≠⇩E u & b ≠⇩E v & [R]u'b) ∨
1273                    (u' =⇩E a & b =⇩E b) ∨
1274                    (u' =⇩E u & b =⇩E v)›
1275            using "β→C"(1)[OF 1, simplified] by simp
1276          moreover {
1277            AOT_assume 0: ‹u' ≠⇩E u & b ≠⇩E v & [R]u'b›
1278            AOT_have ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv')›
1279              using B[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E", OF gv'].
1280            AOT_hence ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R]ub)›
1281              using v'_eq_b "rule=E" by fast
1282            AOT_hence ‹∃u ([F]u & [R]ub & ∀t ([F]t & [R]tb → t =⇩E u))›
1283              using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by fast
1284            then AOT_obtain s where
1285              s_prop: ‹[F]s & [R]sb & ∀t ([F]t & [R]tb → t =⇩E s)›
1286              using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by meson
1287            AOT_have ‹u' =⇩E s›
1288              using s_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E"]
1289                    fu'_R1u'v'[THEN "&E"(1)] 0[THEN "&E"(2)]
1290              by (metis "&I" "→E")
1291            moreover AOT_have ‹u =⇩E s›
1292              using s_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E"] fu Rub
1293              by (metis "&I" "→E")
1294            ultimately AOT_have ‹u' =⇩E u›
1295              by (metis "&I" "ord=Eequiv:2" "ord=Eequiv:3" "→E")
1296            moreover AOT_have ‹¬(u' =⇩E u)›
1297              using 0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)] by (metis "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E") 
1298            ultimately AOT_have ‹u' =⇩E a›
1299              by (metis "raa-cor:3")
1300          }
1301          moreover {
1302            AOT_assume ‹u' =⇩E u & b =⇩E v›
1303            AOT_hence ‹u' =⇩E a›
1304              by (metis "&E"(2) not_b_eq_v "reductio-aa:1")
1305          }
1306          ultimately AOT_show ‹u' =⇩E a›
1307            by (metis "&E"(1) "∨E"(3) "reductio-aa:1") 
1308        qed
1309      }
1310      ultimately AOT_show ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R⇩1]uv')›
1311        by (metis "raa-cor:1")
1312    qed
1313    ultimately AOT_have ‹∃R R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v›
1314      using 1 by blast
1315  }
1316  ultimately AOT_have ‹∃R R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v›
1317    using R_prop by (metis "reductio-aa:2") 
1318  AOT_thus ‹[F]⇧-⇧u ≈⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v›
1319    by (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
1320qed

1323AOT_theorem "P'-eq": ‹[F]⇧-⇧u ≈⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v & [F]u & [G]v → F ≈⇩E G›
1324proof(safe intro!: "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2);
1325      frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
1326  AOT_have ‹[λz [Π]z & z ≠⇩E κ]↓› for Π κ by "cqt:2[lambda]"
1327  note Π_minus_κI = "rule-id-df:2:b[2]"[
1328      where τ=‹(λ(Π, κ). «[Π]⇧-⇧κ»)›, simplified, OF "F-u", simplified, OF this]
1329   and Π_minus_κE = "rule-id-df:2:a[2]"[
1330   where τ=‹(λ(Π, κ). «[Π]⇧-⇧κ»)›, simplified, OF "F-u", simplified, OF this]
1331  AOT_have Π_minus_κ_den: ‹[Π]⇧-⇧κ↓› for Π κ
1332    by (rule Π_minus_κI) "cqt:2[lambda]"+
1333
1334  AOT_have Π_minus_κE1: ‹[Π]κ'›
1335       and Π_minus_κE2: ‹κ' ≠⇩E κ› if ‹[[Π]⇧-⇧κ]κ'› for Π κ κ'
1336  proof -
1337    AOT_have ‹[λz [Π]z & z ≠⇩E κ]κ'›
1338      using Π_minus_κE that by fast
1339    AOT_hence ‹[Π]κ' & κ' ≠⇩E κ›
1340      by (rule "β→C"(1))
1341    AOT_thus ‹[Π]κ'› and ‹κ' ≠⇩E κ›
1342      using "&E" by blast+
1343  qed
1344  AOT_have Π_minus_κI': ‹[[Π]⇧-⇧κ]κ'› if ‹[Π]κ'› and ‹κ' ≠⇩E κ› for Π κ κ'
1345  proof -
1346    AOT_have κ'_den: ‹κ'↓›
1347      by (metis "russell-axiom[exe,1].ψ_denotes_asm" that(1))
1348    AOT_have ‹[λz [Π]z & z ≠⇩E κ]κ'›
1349      by (safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" κ'_den "&I" that)
1350    AOT_thus ‹[[Π]⇧-⇧κ]κ'›
1351      using Π_minus_κI by fast
1352  qed
1353
1354  AOT_assume Gv: ‹[G]v›
1355  AOT_assume Fu: ‹[F]u›
1356  AOT_assume ‹[F]⇧-⇧u ≈⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v›
1357  AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v›
1358    using "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
1359  then AOT_obtain R where R_prop: ‹R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E [G]⇧-⇧v›
1360    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1361  AOT_hence Fact1: ‹∀r([[F]⇧-⇧u]r → ∃!s ([[G]⇧-⇧v]s & [R]rs))›
1362        and Fact1': ‹∀s([[G]⇧-⇧v]s → ∃!r ([[F]⇧-⇧u]r & [R]rs))›
1363    using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
1364  AOT_have ‹R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE [G]⇧-⇧v›
1365    using "equi-rem-thm"[unvarify F G, OF Π_minus_κ_den, OF Π_minus_κ_den,
1366                         THEN "≡E"(1), OF R_prop].
1367  AOT_hence ‹R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟶E [G]⇧-⇧v & R |: [F]⇧-⇧u ⟶⇩o⇩n⇩t⇩oE [G]⇧-⇧v›
1368    using "equi-rem:4"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
1369  AOT_hence Fact2:
1370    ‹∀r∀s∀t(([[F]⇧-⇧u]r & [[F]⇧-⇧u]s & [[G]⇧-⇧v]t) → ([R]rt & [R]st → r =⇩E s))›
1371    using "equi-rem:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
1372
1373  let ?R = ‹«[λxy ([[F]⇧-⇧u]x & [[G]⇧-⇧v]y & [R]xy) ∨ (x =⇩E u & y =⇩E v)]»›
1374  AOT_have R_den: ‹«?R»↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
1375
1376  AOT_show ‹F ≈⇩E G›
1377  proof(safe intro!: "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "∃I"(1)[where τ="?R"] R_den
1378                     "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2" Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1379    fix r
1380    AOT_assume Fr: ‹[F]r›
1381    {
1382      AOT_assume not_r_eq_u: ‹¬(r =⇩E u)›
1383      AOT_hence r_noteq_u: ‹r ≠⇩E u›
1384        using "≡E"(2) "thm-neg=E" by blast
1385      AOT_have ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]r›
1386        by(rule Π_minus_κI; safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" Fr r_noteq_u)
1387      AOT_hence ‹∃!s ([[G]⇧-⇧v]s & [R]rs)›
1388        using Fact1[THEN "∀E"(2)] "→E" Ordinary.ψ by blast
1389      AOT_hence ‹∃s ([[G]⇧-⇧v]s & [R]rs & ∀t ([[G]⇧-⇧v]t & [R]rt → t =⇩E s))›
1390        using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by simp
1391      then AOT_obtain s where s_prop: ‹[[G]⇧-⇧v]s & [R]rs & ∀t ([[G]⇧-⇧v]t & [R]rt → t =⇩E s)›
1392        using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by meson
1393      AOT_hence G_minus_v_s: ‹[[G]⇧-⇧v]s› and Rrs: ‹[R]rs›
1394        using "&E" by blast+
1395      AOT_have s_unique: ‹t =⇩E s› if ‹[[G]⇧-⇧v]t› and ‹[R]rt› for t
1396        using s_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF that].
1397      AOT_have Gs: ‹[G]s›
1398        using Π_minus_κE1[OF G_minus_v_s].
1399      AOT_have s_noteq_v: ‹s ≠⇩E v›
1400        using Π_minus_κE2[OF G_minus_v_s].
1401      AOT_have ‹∃s ([G]s & [«?R»]rs & (∀t ([G]t & [«?R»]rt → t =⇩E s)))›
1402      proof(safe intro!: "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=s] "&I" Gs Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1403        AOT_show ‹[«?R»]rs›
1404          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" "∨I"(1) Π_minus_κI' Fr Gs
1405                           s_noteq_v Rrs r_noteq_u
1406                   simp: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")
1407      next
1408        fix t
1409        AOT_assume 0: ‹[G]t & [«?R»]rt›
1410        AOT_hence ‹([[F]⇧-⇧u]r & [[G]⇧-⇧v]t & [R]rt) ∨ (r =⇩E u & t =⇩E v)›
1411          using "β→C"(1)[OF 0[THEN "&E"(2)], simplified] by blast
1412        AOT_hence 1: ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]r & [[G]⇧-⇧v]t & [R]rt›
1413          using not_r_eq_u by (metis "&E"(1) "∨E"(3) "reductio-aa:1")
1414        AOT_show ‹t =⇩E s› using s_unique 1 "&E" by blast
1415      qed
1416    }
1417    moreover {
1418      AOT_assume r_eq_u: ‹r =⇩E u›
1419      AOT_have ‹∃s ([G]s & [«?R»]rs & (∀t ([G]t & [«?R»]rt → t =⇩E s)))›
1420      proof(safe intro!: "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=v] "&I" Gv Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1421        AOT_show ‹[«?R»]rv›
1422          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" "∨I"(2) Π_minus_κI' Fr r_eq_u
1423                           "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E"] Ordinary.ψ
1424                   simp: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")
1425      next
1426        fix t

1428        AOT_hence ‹([[F]⇧-⇧u]r & [[G]⇧-⇧v]t & [R]rt) ∨ (r =⇩E u & t =⇩E v)›
1429          using "β→C"(1)[OF 0[THEN "&E"(2)], simplified] by blast
1430        AOT_hence ‹r =⇩E u & t =⇩E v›

1432          by (metis "&E"(1) "∨E"(2) "≡E"(1) "reductio-aa:1" "thm-neg=E")
1433        AOT_thus ‹t =⇩E v› using "&E" by blast
1434      qed
1435    }
1436    ultimately AOT_show ‹∃!s ([G]s & [«?R»]rs)›
1437      using "reductio-aa:2" "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by fast
1438  next
1439    fix s
1440    AOT_assume Gs: ‹[G]s›
1441
1442    {

1444      AOT_hence s_noteq_v: ‹s ≠⇩E v›
1445        using "≡E"(2) "thm-neg=E" by blast
1446      AOT_have ‹[[G]⇧-⇧v]s›
1447        by (rule Π_minus_κI; auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" Gs s_noteq_v)

1449        using Fact1'[THEN "Ordinary.∀E"] "→E" by blast

1451        using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by simp
1452      then AOT_obtain r where
1453        r_prop: ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]r & [R]rs & ∀t ([[F]⇧-⇧u]t & [R]ts → t =⇩E r)›
1454        using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by meson
1455      AOT_hence F_minus_u_r: ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]r› and Rrs: ‹[R]rs›
1456        using "&E" by blast+
1457      AOT_have r_unique: ‹t =⇩E r› if ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]t› and ‹[R]ts› for t

1459                     THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF that].

1465      proof(safe intro!: "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=r] "&I" Fr Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1466        AOT_show ‹[«?R»]rs›
1467          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" "∨I"(1) Π_minus_κI' Fr
1468                           Gs s_noteq_v Rrs r_noteq_u
1469                   simp: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")
1470      next
1471        fix t
1472        AOT_assume 0: ‹[F]t & [«?R»]ts›
1473        AOT_hence ‹([[F]⇧-⇧u]t & [[G]⇧-⇧v]s & [R]ts) ∨ (t =⇩E u & s =⇩E v)›
1474          using "β→C"(1)[OF 0[THEN "&E"(2)], simplified] by blast
1475        AOT_hence 1: ‹[[F]⇧-⇧u]t & [[G]⇧-⇧v]s & [R]ts›
1476          using not_s_eq_v by (metis "&E"(2) "∨E"(3) "reductio-aa:1")
1477        AOT_show ‹t =⇩E r› using r_unique 1 "&E" by blast
1478      qed
1479    }
1480    moreover {

1482      AOT_have ‹∃r ([F]r & [«?R»]rs & (∀t ([F]t & [«?R»]ts → t =⇩E r)))›
1483      proof(safe intro!: "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=u] "&I" Fu Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1484        AOT_show ‹[«?R»]us›
1485          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" prod_denotesI "∨I"(2)
1486                            Π_minus_κI' Gs s_eq_v Ordinary.ψ
1487                            "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E"])
1488      next
1489        fix t
1490        AOT_assume 0: ‹[F]t & [«?R»]ts›
1491        AOT_hence 1: ‹([[F]⇧-⇧u]t & [[G]⇧-⇧v]s & [R]ts) ∨ (t =⇩E u & s =⇩E v)›
1492          using "β→C"(1)[OF 0[THEN "&E"(2)], simplified] by blast
1493        moreover AOT_have ‹¬([[F]⇧-⇧u]t & [[G]⇧-⇧v]s & [R]ts)›
1494        proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
1495          AOT_assume ‹([[F]⇧-⇧u]t & [[G]⇧-⇧v]s & [R]ts)›
1496          AOT_hence ‹[[G]⇧-⇧v]s› using "&E" by blast
1497          AOT_thus ‹s =⇩E v & ¬(s =⇩E v)›
1498            by (metis Π_minus_κE2 "≡E"(4) "reductio-aa:1" s_eq_v "thm-neg=E")
1499        qed
1500        ultimately AOT_have ‹t =⇩E u & s =⇩E v›
1501          by (metis "∨E"(2))
1502        AOT_thus ‹t =⇩E u› using "&E" by blast
1503      qed
1504    }
1505    ultimately AOT_show ‹∃!r ([F]r & [«?R»]rs)›
1506      using "≡E"(2) "equi:1" "reductio-aa:2" by fast
1507  qed
1508qed

1511AOT_theorem "approx-cont:1": ‹∃F∃G ◇(F ≈⇩E G & ◇¬F ≈⇩E G)›
1512proof -
1513  let ?P = ‹«[λx E!x & ¬❙𝒜E!x]»›
1514  AOT_have ‹◇q⇩0 & ◇¬q⇩0› by (metis q⇩0_prop)
1515  AOT_hence 1: ‹◇∃x(E!x & ¬❙𝒜E!x) & ◇¬∃x(E!x & ¬❙𝒜E!x)›
1516    by (rule q⇩0_def[THEN "=⇩d⇩fE"(2), rotated])
1517       (simp add: "log-prop-prop:2")
1518  AOT_have θ: ‹◇∃x [«?P»]x & ◇¬∃x [«?P»]x›
1519    apply (AOT_subst ‹[«?P»]x› ‹E!x & ¬❙𝒜E!x› for: x)
1520     apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
1521    by (fact 1)
1522  show ?thesis
1523  proof (rule "∃I"(1))+

1637    by (fact 1)

1744notepad
1745begin
1746  text‹We already have defined being equivalent on the ordinary objects in the
1747       Extended Relation Comprehension theory.›
1748  AOT_have ‹F ≡⇩E G ≡⇩d⇩f F↓ & G↓ & ∀u ([F]u ≡ [G]u)› for F G
1749    using eqE by blast

1752AOT_theorem "apE-eqE:1": ‹F ≡⇩E G → F ≈⇩E G›
1753proof(rule "→I")
1754  AOT_assume 0: ‹F ≡⇩E G›
1755  AOT_have ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
1756  proof (safe intro!: "∃I"(1)[where τ="«(=⇩E)»"] "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I"
1757                      "=E[denotes]" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.GEN
1758                      "→I" "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
1759    fix u
1760    AOT_assume Fu: ‹[F]u›
1761    AOT_hence Gu: ‹[G]u›
1762      using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF eqE, OF 0, THEN "&E"(2),
1763                   THEN "Ordinary.∀E"[where α=u], THEN "≡E"(1)]
1764            Ordinary.ψ Fu by blast
1765    AOT_show ‹∃v ([G]v & u =⇩E v & ∀v' ([G]v' & u =⇩E v' → v' =⇩E v))›
1766      by (safe intro!: "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=u] "&I" GEN "→I" Ordinary.ψ Gu
1767                       "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Ordinary.ψ]
1768                       "ord=Eequiv:2"[THEN "→E"] dest!: "&E"(2))
1769  next
1770    fix v
1771    AOT_assume Gv: ‹[G]v›
1772    AOT_hence Fv: ‹[F]v›
1773      using "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF eqE, OF 0, THEN "&E"(2),
1774                   THEN "Ordinary.∀E"[where α=v], THEN "≡E"(2)]
1775            Ordinary.ψ Gv by blast
1776    AOT_show ‹∃u ([F]u & u =⇩E v & ∀v' ([F]v' & v' =⇩E v → v' =⇩E u))›
1777      by (safe intro!: "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=v] "&I" GEN "→I" Ordinary.ψ Fv
1778                       "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Ordinary.ψ]
1779                       "ord=Eequiv:2"[THEN "→E"] dest!: "&E"(2))
1780  qed
1781  AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E G›
1782    by (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
1783qed
1784
1785AOT_theorem "apE-eqE:2": ‹(F ≈⇩E G & G ≡⇩E H) → F ≈⇩E H›
1786proof(rule "→I")
1787  AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E G & G ≡⇩E H›
1788  AOT_hence ‹F ≈⇩E G› and ‹G ≈⇩E H›
1789    using "apE-eqE:1"[THEN "→E"] "&E" by blast+
1790  AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E H›
1791    by (metis Adjunction "eq-part:3" "vdash-properties:10")
1792qed

1795AOT_act_theorem "eq-part-act:1": ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≡⇩E F›
1796proof (safe intro!: eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2" Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1797  fix u
1798  AOT_have ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u ≡ ❙𝒜[F]u›
1799    by (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
1800  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ [F]u›
1801    using "act-conj-act:4" "logic-actual"[act_axiom_inst, THEN "→E"] by blast
1802  finally AOT_show ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u ≡ [F]u›.
1803qed

1809AOT_theorem "actuallyF:1": ‹❙𝒜(F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
1810proof -
1811  AOT_have 1: ‹❙𝒜([F]x ≡ ❙𝒜[F]x)› for x
1812    by (meson "Act-Basic:5" "act-conj-act:4" "≡E"(2) "Commutativity of ≡")
1813  AOT_have ‹❙𝒜([F]x ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]x)› for x
1814    apply (AOT_subst ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]x› ‹❙𝒜[F]x›)
1815     apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
1816     apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
1817    by (fact 1)
1818  AOT_hence ‹O!x → ❙𝒜([F]x ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]x)› for x
1819    by (metis "→I") 
1820  AOT_hence ‹∀u ❙𝒜([F]u ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u)›
1821    using "∀I" by fast
1822  AOT_hence 1: ‹❙𝒜∀u ([F]u ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u)›
1823    by (metis "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[2]" "→E")
1824  AOT_modally_strict {
1825    AOT_have ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› by "cqt:2"
1826  } note 2 = this
1827  AOT_have ‹❙𝒜(F ≡⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
1828    apply (AOT_subst ‹F ≡⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]› ‹∀u ([F]u ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u)›)
1829    using eqE[THEN "≡Df", THEN "≡S"(1), OF "&I",
1830              OF "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst], OF 2]
1831    by (auto simp: 1)
1832  moreover AOT_have ‹❙𝒜(F ≡⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] → F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
1833    using "apE-eqE:1"[unvarify G, THEN "RA[2]", OF 2] by metis
1834  ultimately AOT_show ‹❙𝒜F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]›
1835    by (metis "act-cond" "→E")
1836qed

1859AOT_theorem "approx-nec:1": ‹Rigid(F) → F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]›
1860proof(rule "→I")
1861  AOT_assume ‹Rigid([F])›
1862  AOT_hence A: ‹□∀x ([F]x → □[F]x)›
1863    using "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)] by blast
1864  AOT_hence 0: ‹∀x □([F]x → □[F]x)›
1865    using CBF[THEN "→E"] by blast
1866  AOT_hence 1: ‹∀x ([F]x → □[F]x)›
1867    using A "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"] by blast
1868  AOT_have act_F_den: ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓›
1869    by "cqt:2"
1870  AOT_show ‹F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]›
1871  proof (safe intro!: "apE-eqE:1"[unvarify G, THEN "→E"] eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I"
1872                      "cqt:2" act_F_den Ordinary.GEN "→I" "≡I")
1873    fix u
1874    AOT_assume ‹[F]u›
1875    AOT_hence ‹□[F]u›
1876      using 1[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
1877    AOT_hence act_F_u: ‹❙𝒜[F]u›
1878      by (metis "nec-imp-act" "→E")
1879    AOT_show ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u›
1880      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" act_F_u)
1881  next
1882    fix u
1883    AOT_assume ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u›
1884    AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[F]u›
1885      by (rule "β→C"(1))
1886    AOT_thus ‹[F]u›
1887      using 0[THEN "∀E"(2)]
1888      by (metis "≡E"(1) "sc-eq-fur:2" "→E")
1889  qed
1890qed

1893AOT_theorem "approx-nec:2":
1894  ‹F ≈⇩E G ≡ ∀H ([λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E G)›
1895proof(rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
1896  AOT_assume 0: ‹F ≈⇩E G›
1897  AOT_assume 0: ‹F ≈⇩E G›
1898  AOT_hence ‹∀H (H ≈⇩E F ≡ H ≈⇩E G)›
1899    using "eq-part:4"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF 0] by blast
1900  AOT_have ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E G› for H
1901    by (rule "∀E"(1)[OF "eq-part:4"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF 0]]) "cqt:2"
1902  AOT_thus ‹∀H ([λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E G)›
1903    by (rule GEN)
1904next
1905  AOT_assume 0: ‹∀H ([λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E G)›
1906  AOT_obtain H where ‹Rigidifies(H,F)›
1907    using "rigid-der:3" "∃E" by metis
1908  AOT_hence H: ‹Rigid(H) & ∀x ([H]x ≡ [F]x)›
1909    using "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
1910  AOT_have H_rigid: ‹□∀x ([H]x → □[H]x)›
1911    using H[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"], THEN "&E"(2)].
1912  AOT_hence ‹∀x □([H]x → □[H]x)›
1913    using "CBF" "vdash-properties:10" by blast
1914  AOT_hence ‹□([H]x → □[H]x)› for x using "∀E"(2) by blast
1915  AOT_hence rigid: ‹[H]x ≡ ❙𝒜[H]x› for x
1916     by (metis "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:3:a" "sc-eq-fur:2" "→E")
1917  AOT_have ‹H ≡⇩E F›
1918  proof (safe intro!: eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2" Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1919    AOT_show ‹[H]u ≡ [F]u› for u using H[THEN "&E"(2)] "∀E"(2) by fast
1920  qed
1921  AOT_hence ‹H ≈⇩E F›
1922    by (rule "apE-eqE:2"[THEN "→E", OF "&I", rotated])
1923       (simp add: "eq-part:1")
1924  AOT_hence F_approx_H: ‹F ≈⇩E H›
1925    by (metis "eq-part:2" "→E")
1926  moreover AOT_have H_eq_act_H: ‹H ≡⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[H]z]›
1927  proof (safe intro!: eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2" Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1928    AOT_show ‹[H]u ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[H]z]u› for u
1929      apply (AOT_subst ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z]u› ‹❙𝒜[H]u›)
1930       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"])
1931       apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
1932      using rigid by blast
1933  qed
1934  AOT_have a: ‹F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[H]z]›
1935    apply (rule "apE-eqE:2"[unvarify H, THEN "→E"])
1936     apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
1937    using F_approx_H H_eq_act_H "&I" by blast
1938  AOT_hence ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E F›
1939    apply (rule "eq-part:2"[unvarify G, THEN "→E", rotated])
1940    by "cqt:2[lambda]"
1941  AOT_hence b: ‹[λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E G›
1942    by (rule 0[THEN "∀E"(1), THEN "≡E"(1), rotated]) "cqt:2" 
1943  AOT_show ‹F ≈⇩E G›
1944    by (rule "eq-part:3"[unvarify G, THEN "→E", rotated, OF "&I", OF a, OF b])
1945       "cqt:2"
1946qed

1948AOT_theorem "approx-nec:3":
1949  ‹(Rigid(F) & Rigid(G)) → □(F ≈⇩E G → □F ≈⇩E G)›
1950proof (rule "→I")
1951  AOT_assume ‹Rigid(F) & Rigid(G)›
1952  AOT_hence ‹□∀x([F]x → □[F]x)› and ‹□∀x([G]x → □[G]x)›
1953    using "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)] "&E" by blast+
1954  AOT_hence ‹□(□∀x([F]x → □[F]x) & □∀x([G]x → □[G]x))›
1955    using "KBasic:3" "4" "&I" "≡E"(2) "vdash-properties:10" by meson
1956  moreover AOT_have ‹□(□∀x([F]x → □[F]x) & □∀x([G]x → □[G]x)) →
1957                     □(F ≈⇩E G → □F ≈⇩E G)›
1958  proof(rule RM; rule "→I"; rule "→I")
1959    AOT_modally_strict {
1960      AOT_assume ‹□∀x([F]x → □[F]x) & □∀x([G]x → □[G]x)›
1961      AOT_hence ‹□∀x([F]x → □[F]x)› and ‹□∀x([G]x → □[G]x)›
1962        using "&E" by blast+
1963      AOT_hence ‹∀x□([F]x → □[F]x)› and ‹∀x□([G]x → □[G]x)›
1964        using CBF[THEN "→E"] by blast+
1965      AOT_hence F_nec: ‹□([F]x → □[F]x)›
1966            and G_nec: ‹□([G]x → □[G]x)› for x
1967        using "∀E"(2) by blast+
1968      AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E G›
1969      AOT_hence ‹∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
1970        by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "equi:3")
1971      then AOT_obtain R where ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
1972        using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1973      AOT_hence C1: ‹∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv))›
1974            and C2: ‹∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv))›
1975        using "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
1976      AOT_obtain R' where ‹Rigidifies(R', R)›
1977        using "rigid-der:3" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1978      AOT_hence 1: ‹Rigid(R') & ∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n ([R']x⇩1...x⇩n ≡ [R]x⇩1...x⇩n)›
1979        using "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
1980      AOT_hence ‹□∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n ([R']x⇩1...x⇩n → □[R']x⇩1...x⇩n)›
1981        using "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
1982      AOT_hence ‹∀x⇩1...∀x⇩n (◇[R']x⇩1...x⇩n → □[R']x⇩1...x⇩n)›
1983        using "≡E"(1) "rigid-rel-thms:1" by blast
1984      AOT_hence D: ‹∀x⇩1∀x⇩2 (◇[R']x⇩1x⇩2 → □[R']x⇩1x⇩2)›
1985        using tuple_forall[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
1986      AOT_have E: ‹∀x⇩1∀x⇩2 ([R']x⇩1x⇩2 ≡ [R]x⇩1x⇩2)›
1987        using tuple_forall[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", OF 1[THEN "&E"(2)]] by blast
1988      AOT_have ‹∀u □([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))›
1989           and ‹∀v □([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›
1990      proof (safe intro!: Ordinary.GEN "→I")
1991        fix u
1992        AOT_show ‹□([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))›
1993        proof (rule "raa-cor:1")
1994          AOT_assume ‹¬□([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))›
1995          AOT_hence 1: ‹◇¬([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))›
1996            using "KBasic:11" "≡E"(1) by blast
1997          AOT_have ‹◇([F]u & ¬∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))›
1998            apply (AOT_subst ‹[F]u & ¬∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)›
1999                             ‹¬([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))›)
2000             apply (meson "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:1:b" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
2001            by (fact 1)
2002          AOT_hence A: ‹◇[F]u & ◇¬∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)›
2003            using "KBasic2:3" "→E" by blast
2004          AOT_hence ‹□[F]u›
2005            using F_nec "&E"(1) "≡E"(1) "sc-eq-box-box:1" "→E" by blast
2006          AOT_hence ‹[F]u›
2007            by (metis "qml:2"[axiom_inst] "→E")
2008          AOT_hence ‹∃!v ([G]v & [R]uv)›
2009            using C1[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E"] by blast
2010          AOT_hence ‹∃v ([G]v & [R]uv & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R]uv' → v' =⇩E v))›
2011            using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by auto
2012          then AOT_obtain a where
2013            a_prop: ‹O!a & ([G]a & [R]ua & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R]uv' → v' =⇩E a))›
2014            using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2015          AOT_have ‹∃v □([G]v & [R']uv & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E v))›
2016          proof(safe intro!: "∃I"(2)[where β=a] "&I" a_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]
2017                             "KBasic:3"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
2018            AOT_show ‹□[G]a›
2019              using a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
2020              by (metis G_nec "qml:2"[axiom_inst] "→E")
2021          next
2022            AOT_show ‹□[R']ua›
2023              using D[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"]
2024                    E[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(2),
2025                      OF a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]]
2026              by (metis "T◇" "→E")
2027          next
2028            AOT_have ‹∀v' □([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E a)›
2029            proof (rule Ordinary.GEN; rule "raa-cor:1")
2030              fix v'
2031              AOT_assume ‹¬□([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E a)›
2032              AOT_hence ‹◇¬([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E a)›
2033                by (metis "KBasic:11" "≡E"(1))
2034              AOT_hence ‹◇([G]v' & [R']uv' & ¬v' =⇩E a)›
2035                by (AOT_subst ‹[G]v' & [R']uv' & ¬v' =⇩E a›
2036                              ‹¬([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E a)›)
2037                   (meson "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:1:b" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
2038              AOT_hence 1: ‹◇[G]v'› and 2: ‹◇[R']uv'› and 3: ‹◇¬v' =⇩E a›
2039                using "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "&E"(1)]
2040                      "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "&E"(2)] by blast+
2041              AOT_have Gv': ‹[G]v'› using G_nec 1
2042                by (meson "B◇" "KBasic:13" "→E")
2043              AOT_have ‹□[R']uv'›
2044                using 2 D[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
2045              AOT_hence R'uv': ‹[R']uv'›
2046                by (metis "B◇" "T◇" "→E") 
2047              AOT_hence ‹[R]uv'›
2048                using E[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2049              AOT_hence ‹v' =⇩E a›
2050                using a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E",
2051                             THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF Gv'] by blast
2052              AOT_hence ‹□(v' =⇩E a)›
2053                by (metis "id-nec3:1" "≡E"(4) "raa-cor:3")
2054              moreover AOT_have ‹¬□(v' =⇩E a)›
2055                using 3 "KBasic:11" "≡E"(2) by blast
2056              ultimately AOT_show ‹□(v' =⇩E a) & ¬□(v' =⇩E a)›
2057                using "&I" by blast
2058            qed
2059            AOT_thus ‹□∀v'([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E a)›
2060              using "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[BF]" "→E" by fast
2061          qed
2062          AOT_hence ‹□∃v ([G]v & [R']uv & ∀v' ([G]v' & [R']uv' → v' =⇩E v))›
2063            using "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[Buridan]" "→E" by fast
2064          AOT_hence ‹□∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)›
2065            by (AOT_subst_thm "equi:1")
2066          moreover AOT_have ‹¬□∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)›
2067            using A[THEN "&E"(2)] "KBasic:11"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2068          ultimately AOT_show ‹□∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv) & ¬□∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)›
2069            by (rule "&I")
2070        qed
2071      next
2072        fix v
2073        AOT_show ‹□([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›
2074        proof (rule "raa-cor:1")
2075          AOT_assume ‹¬□([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›
2076          AOT_hence 1: ‹◇¬([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›
2077            using "KBasic:11" "≡E"(1) by blast
2078          AOT_hence ‹◇([G]v & ¬∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›
2079            by (AOT_subst ‹[G]v & ¬∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)›
2080                          ‹¬([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›)
2081               (meson "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:1:b" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
2082          AOT_hence A: ‹◇[G]v & ◇¬∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)›
2083            using "KBasic2:3" "→E" by blast
2084          AOT_hence ‹□[G]v›
2085            using G_nec "&E"(1) "≡E"(1) "sc-eq-box-box:1" "→E" by blast
2086          AOT_hence ‹[G]v› by (metis "qml:2"[axiom_inst] "→E")
2087          AOT_hence ‹∃!u ([F]u & [R]uv)›
2088            using C2[THEN "Ordinary.∀E", THEN "→E"] by blast
2089          AOT_hence ‹∃u ([F]u & [R]uv & ∀u' ([F]u' & [R]u'v → u' =⇩E u))›
2090            using "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by auto
2091          then AOT_obtain a where
2092              a_prop: ‹O!a & ([F]a & [R]av & ∀u' ([F]u' & [R]u'v → u' =⇩E a))›
2093            using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2094          AOT_have ‹∃u □([F]u & [R']uv & ∀u' ([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E u))›
2095          proof(safe intro!: "∃I"(2)[where β=a] "&I" a_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]
2096                             "KBasic:3"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
2097            AOT_show ‹□[F]a›
2098              using a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
2099              by (metis F_nec "qml:2"[axiom_inst] "→E")
2100          next
2101            AOT_show ‹□[R']av›
2102              using D[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"]
2103                    E[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(2),
2104                      OF a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]]
2105              by (metis "T◇" "→E")
2106          next
2107            AOT_have ‹∀u' □([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E a)›
2108            proof (rule Ordinary.GEN; rule "raa-cor:1")
2109              fix u'
2110              AOT_assume ‹¬□([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E a)›
2111              AOT_hence ‹◇¬([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E a)›
2112                by (metis "KBasic:11" "≡E"(1))
2113              AOT_hence ‹◇([F]u' & [R']u'v & ¬u' =⇩E a)›
2114                by (AOT_subst ‹[F]u' & [R']u'v & ¬u' =⇩E a›
2115                              ‹¬([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E a)›)
2116                   (meson "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:1:b" "oth-class-taut:3:a")
2117              AOT_hence 1: ‹◇[F]u'› and 2: ‹◇[R']u'v› and 3: ‹◇¬u' =⇩E a›
2118                using "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "&E"(1)]
2119                      "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "&E"(2)] by blast+
2120              AOT_have Fu': ‹[F]u'› using F_nec 1
2121                by (meson "B◇" "KBasic:13" "→E")
2122              AOT_have ‹□[R']u'v›
2123                using 2 D[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
2124              AOT_hence R'u'v: ‹[R']u'v›
2125                by (metis "B◇" "T◇" "→E") 
2126              AOT_hence ‹[R]u'v›
2127                using E[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2128              AOT_hence ‹u' =⇩E a›
2129                using a_prop[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "&E"(2), THEN "Ordinary.∀E",
2130                             THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF Fu'] by blast
2131              AOT_hence ‹□(u' =⇩E a)›
2132                by (metis "id-nec3:1" "≡E"(4) "raa-cor:3")
2133              moreover AOT_have ‹¬□(u' =⇩E a)›
2134                using 3 "KBasic:11" "≡E"(2) by blast
2135              ultimately AOT_show ‹□(u' =⇩E a) & ¬□(u' =⇩E a)›
2136                using "&I" by blast
2137            qed
2138            AOT_thus ‹□∀u'([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E a)›
2139              using "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[BF]" "→E" by fast
2140          qed
2141          AOT_hence 1: ‹□∃u ([F]u & [R']uv & ∀u' ([F]u' & [R']u'v → u' =⇩E u))›
2142            using "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[Buridan]" "→E" by fast
2143          AOT_hence ‹□∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)›
2144            by (AOT_subst_thm "equi:1")
2145          moreover AOT_have ‹¬□∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)›
2146            using A[THEN "&E"(2)] "KBasic:11"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2147          ultimately AOT_show ‹□∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv) & ¬□∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)›
2148            by (rule "&I")
2149        qed
2150      qed
2151      AOT_hence ‹□∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv))›
2152            and ‹□∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv))›
2153        using "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[BF]"[THEN "→E"] by auto
2154      moreover AOT_have ‹□[R']↓› and ‹□[F]↓› and ‹□[G]↓›
2155        by (simp_all add: "ex:2:a")
2156      ultimately AOT_have ‹□([R']↓ & [F]↓ & [G]↓ & ∀u ([F]u → ∃!v ([G]v & [R']uv)) &
2157                                                   ∀v ([G]v → ∃!u ([F]u & [R']uv)))›
2158        using "KBasic:3" "&I" "≡E"(2) by meson
2159      AOT_hence ‹□R' |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
2160        by (AOT_subst_def "equi:2")
2161      AOT_hence ‹∃R □R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
2162        by (rule "∃I"(2))
2163      AOT_hence ‹□∃R R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G›
2164        by (metis Buridan "→E")
2165      AOT_thus ‹□F ≈⇩E G›
2166        by (AOT_subst_def "equi:3")
2167    }
2168  qed
2169  ultimately AOT_show ‹□(F ≈⇩E G → □F ≈⇩E G)›
2170    using "→E" by blast
2171qed
2172

2174AOT_define numbers :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (‹Numbers'(_,_')›)
2175  ‹Numbers(x,G) ≡⇩d⇩f A!x & G↓ & ∀F(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›

2177AOT_theorem "numbers[den]":
2178  ‹Π↓ → (Numbers(κ, Π) ≡ A!κ & ∀F(κ[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E Π))›
2179  apply (safe intro!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "≡I" "→I" "cqt:2"
2180               dest!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"])

2183AOT_theorem "num-tran:1":
2184  ‹G ≈⇩E H → (Numbers(x, G) ≡ Numbers(x, H))›
2185proof (safe intro!: "→I" "≡I")
2186  AOT_assume 0: ‹G ≈⇩E H›
2187  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, G)›
2188  AOT_hence Ax: ‹A!x› and θ: ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2189    using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
2190  AOT_show ‹Numbers(x, H)›
2191  proof(safe intro!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" Ax "cqt:2" GEN)
2192    fix F
2193    AOT_have ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G›
2194      using θ[THEN "∀E"(2)].
2195    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H›
2196      using 0 "approx-nec:2"[THEN "≡E"(1), THEN "∀E"(2)] by metis
2197    finally AOT_show ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H›.
2198  qed
2199next
2200  AOT_assume ‹G ≈⇩E H›
2201  AOT_hence 0: ‹H ≈⇩E G›
2202    by (metis "eq-part:2" "→E")
2203  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, H)›
2204  AOT_hence Ax: ‹A!x› and θ: ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H)›
2205    using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
2206  AOT_show ‹Numbers(x, G)›
2207  proof(safe intro!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" Ax "cqt:2"  GEN)
2208    fix F
2209    AOT_have ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H›
2210      using θ[THEN "∀E"(2)].
2211    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G›
2212      using 0 "approx-nec:2"[THEN "≡E"(1), THEN "∀E"(2)] by metis
2213    finally AOT_show ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G›.
2214  qed
2215qed

2217AOT_theorem "num-tran:2":
2218  ‹(Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(x,H)) → G ≈⇩E H›
2219proof (rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
2220  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x,G)›
2221  AOT_hence ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2222    using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
2223  AOT_hence 1: ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G› for F
2224    using "∀E"(2) by blast
2225  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x,H)›
2226  AOT_hence ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H)›
2227    using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
2228  AOT_hence ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H› for F
2229    using "∀E"(2) by blast
2230  AOT_hence ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H› for F
2231    by (metis "1" "≡E"(6))
2232  AOT_thus ‹G ≈⇩E H›
2233    using "approx-nec:2"[THEN "≡E"(2), OF GEN] by blast
2234qed

2240AOT_theorem "pre-Hume":
2241  ‹(Numbers(x,G) & Numbers(y,H)) → (x = y ≡ G ≈⇩E H)›
2242proof(safe intro!: "→I" "≡I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
2243  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, G)›
2244  moreover AOT_assume ‹x = y›
2245  ultimately AOT_have ‹Numbers(y, G)› by (rule "rule=E")
2246  moreover AOT_assume ‹Numbers(y, H)›
2247  ultimately AOT_show ‹G ≈⇩E H› using "num-tran:2" "→E" "&I" by blast
2248next
2249  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, G)›
2250  AOT_hence Ax: ‹A!x› and xF: ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2251    using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
2252  AOT_assume ‹Numbers(y, H)›
2253  AOT_hence Ay: ‹A!y› and yF: ‹∀F (y[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H)›
2254    using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
2255  AOT_assume G_approx_H: ‹G ≈⇩E H›
2256  AOT_show ‹x = y›
2257  proof(rule "ab-obey:1"[THEN "→E", THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF Ax, OF Ay]; rule GEN)
2258    fix F
2259    AOT_have ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G›
2260      using xF[THEN "∀E"(2)].
2261    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E H›
2262      using "approx-nec:2"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF G_approx_H, THEN "∀E"(2)].
2263    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ y[F]›
2264      using yF[THEN "∀E"(2), symmetric].
2265    finally AOT_show ‹x[F] ≡ y[F]›.
2266  qed
2267qed
