2269AOT_theorem "two-num-not":
2270  ‹∃u∃v(u ≠ v) → ∃x∃G∃H(Numbers(x,G) & Numbers(x, H) & ¬G ≡⇩E H)›
2271proof (rule "→I")
2272  AOT_have eqE_den: ‹[λx x =⇩E y]↓› for y by "cqt:2"
2273  AOT_assume ‹∃u∃v(u ≠ v)›
2274  then AOT_obtain c where Oc: ‹O!c› and ‹∃v (c ≠ v)›
2275    using "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2276  then AOT_obtain d where Od: ‹O!d› and c_noteq_d: ‹c ≠ d›
2277    using "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2278  AOT_hence c_noteqE_d: ‹c ≠⇩E d›
2279    using "=E-simple:2"[THEN "→E"] "=E-simple:2" "≡E"(2) "modus-tollens:1"
2280          "=-infix" "≡⇩d⇩fE" "thm-neg=E" by fast
2281  AOT_hence not_c_eqE_d: ‹¬c =⇩E d›
2282    using "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E" by blast
2283  AOT_have ‹∃x (A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λx x =⇩E c]))›
2284    by (simp add: "A-objects"[axiom_inst])
2285  then AOT_obtain a where a_prop: ‹A!a & ∀F (a[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λx x =⇩E c])›
2286    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2287  AOT_have ‹∃x (A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λx x =⇩E d]))›
2288    by (simp add: "A-objects" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
2289  then AOT_obtain b where b_prop: ‹A!b & ∀F (b[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λx x =⇩E d])›
2290    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2291  AOT_have num_a_eq_c: ‹Numbers(a, [λx x =⇩E c])›
2292    by (safe intro!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" a_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]
2293                     a_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]) "cqt:2"
2294  moreover AOT_have num_b_eq_d: ‹Numbers(b, [λx x =⇩E d])›
2295    by (safe intro!: numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" b_prop[THEN "&E"(1)]
2296                     b_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]) "cqt:2"
2297  moreover AOT_have ‹[λx x =⇩E c] ≈⇩E [λx x =⇩E d]›
2298  proof (rule "equi:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
2299    let ?R = ‹«[λxy (x =⇩E c & y =⇩E d)]»›
2300    AOT_have Rcd: ‹[«?R»]cd›
2301      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" prod_denotesI
2302                       "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E"] Od Oc)
2303    AOT_show ‹∃R R |: [λx x =⇩E c] ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E [λx x =⇩E d]›
2304    proof (safe intro!: "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹?R›] "equi:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I"
2305                        eqE_den Ordinary.GEN "→I")
2306      AOT_show ‹«?R»↓› by "cqt:2"
2307    next
2308      fix u
2309      AOT_assume ‹[λx x =⇩E c]u›
2310      AOT_hence ‹u =⇩E c›
2311        by (metis "β→C"(1))
2312      AOT_hence u_is_c: ‹u = c›
2313        by (metis "=E-simple:2" "→E")
2314      AOT_show ‹∃!v ([λx x =⇩E d]v & [«?R»]uv)›
2315      proof (safe intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "∃I"(2)[where β=d] "&I"
2316                          Od Ordinary.GEN "→I")
2317        AOT_show ‹[λx x =⇩E d]d›
2318          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Od])
2319      next
2320        AOT_show ‹[«?R»]ud›
2321          using u_is_c[symmetric] Rcd "rule=E" by fast
2322      next
2323        fix v
2324        AOT_assume ‹[λx x =⇩E d]v & [«?R»]uv›
2325        AOT_thus ‹v =⇩E d›
2326          by (metis "β→C"(1) "&E"(1))
2327      qed
2328    next
2329      fix v
2330      AOT_assume ‹[λx x =⇩E d]v›
2331      AOT_hence ‹v =⇩E d›
2332        by (metis "β→C"(1))
2333      AOT_hence v_is_d: ‹v = d›
2334        by (metis "=E-simple:2" "→E")
2335      AOT_show ‹∃!u ([λx x =⇩E c]u & [«?R»]uv)›
2336      proof (safe intro!: "equi:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "∃I"(2)[where β=c] "&I"
2337                          Oc Ordinary.GEN "→I")
2338        AOT_show ‹[λx x =⇩E c]c›
2339          by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Oc])
2340      next
2341        AOT_show ‹[«?R»]cv›
2342          using v_is_d[symmetric] Rcd "rule=E" by fast
2343      next
2344        fix u
2345        AOT_assume ‹[λx x =⇩E c]u & [«?R»]uv›
2346        AOT_thus ‹u =⇩E c›
2347          by (metis "β→C"(1) "&E"(1))
2348      qed
2349    next
2350      AOT_show ‹«?R»↓›
2351        by "cqt:2"
2352    qed
2353  qed
2354  ultimately AOT_have ‹a = b›
2355    using "pre-Hume"[unvarify G H, OF eqE_den, OF eqE_den, THEN "→E",
2356                     OF "&I", THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2357  AOT_hence num_a_eq_d: ‹Numbers(a, [λx x =⇩E d])›
2358    using num_b_eq_d "rule=E" id_sym by fast
2359  AOT_have not_equiv: ‹¬[λx x =⇩E c] ≡⇩E [λx x =⇩E d]›
2360  proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
2361    AOT_assume ‹[λx x =⇩E c] ≡⇩E [λx x =⇩E d]›
2362    AOT_hence ‹[λx x =⇩E c]c ≡ [λx x =⇩E d]c›
2363      using eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] Oc by blast
2364    moreover AOT_have ‹[λx x =⇩E c]c›
2365      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Oc])
2366    ultimately AOT_have ‹[λx x =⇩E d]c›
2367      using "≡E"(1) by blast
2368    AOT_hence ‹c =⇩E d›
2369      by (rule "β→C"(1))
2370    AOT_thus ‹c =⇩E d & ¬c =⇩E d›
2371      using not_c_eqE_d "&I" by blast
2372  qed
2373  AOT_show ‹∃x ∃G ∃H (Numbers(x,G) & Numbers(x,H) & ¬G ≡⇩E H)›
2374    apply (rule "∃I"(2)[where β=a])
2375    apply (rule "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«[λx x =⇩E c]»›])
2376     apply (rule "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«[λx x =⇩E d]»›])
2377    by (safe intro!: eqE_den "&I" num_a_eq_c num_a_eq_d not_equiv)
2378qed

2390AOT_theorem "num-cont:1":
2391  ‹∃x∃G(Numbers(x, G) & ¬□Numbers(x, G))›
2392proof -
2393  AOT_have ‹∃F∃G ◇([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G & ◇¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2394    using "approx-cont:2".
2395  then AOT_obtain F where ‹∃G ◇([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G & ◇¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2396    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2397  then AOT_obtain G where ‹◇([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G & ◇¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2398    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2399  AOT_hence θ: ‹◇[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G› and ζ: ‹◇¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G›
2400    using "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E"] "&E" "4◇"[THEN "→E"] by blast+
2401  AOT_obtain a where ‹Numbers(a, G)›
2402    using "num:1" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2403  moreover AOT_have ‹¬□Numbers(a, G)›
2404  proof (rule "raa-cor:2")
2405    AOT_assume ‹□Numbers(a, G)›
2406    AOT_hence ‹□([A!]a & G↓ & ∀F (a[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G))›
2407      by (AOT_subst_def (reverse) numbers)
2408    AOT_hence ‹□A!a› and ‹□∀F (a[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2409      using "KBasic:3"[THEN "≡E"(1)] "&E" by blast+
2410    AOT_hence ‹∀F □(a[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2411      using CBF[THEN "→E"] by blast
2412    AOT_hence ‹□(a[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2413      using "∀E"(2) by blast
2414    AOT_hence A: ‹□(a[F] → [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2415          and B: ‹□([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G → a[F])›
2416      using "KBasic:4"[THEN "≡E"(1)] "&E" by blast+
2417    AOT_have ‹□(¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G → ¬a[F])›
2418      apply (AOT_subst ‹¬[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G → ¬a[F]› ‹a[F] → [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G›)
2419       using "≡I" "useful-tautologies:4" "useful-tautologies:5" apply presburger
2420       by (fact A)
2421     AOT_hence ‹◇¬a[F]›
2422       by (metis "KBasic:13" ζ "→E")
2423    AOT_hence ‹¬a[F]›
2424      by (metis "KBasic:11" "en-eq:2[1]" "≡E"(2) "≡E"(4))
2425    AOT_hence ‹¬◇a[F]›
2426      by (metis "en-eq:3[1]" "≡E"(4))
2427    moreover AOT_have ‹◇a[F]›
2428      by (meson B θ "KBasic:13" "→E")
2429    ultimately AOT_show ‹◇a[F] & ¬◇a[F]›
2430      using "&I" by blast
2431  qed
2432
2433  ultimately AOT_have ‹Numbers(a, G) & ¬□Numbers(a, G)›
2434    using "&I" by blast
2435  AOT_hence ‹∃G (Numbers(a, G) & ¬□Numbers(a, G))›
2436    by (rule "∃I")
2437  AOT_thus ‹∃x∃G (Numbers(x, G) & ¬□Numbers(x, G))›
2438    by (rule "∃I")
2439qed

2441AOT_theorem "num-cont:2":
2442  ‹Rigid(G) → □∀x(Numbers(x,G) → □Numbers(x,G))›
2443proof(rule "→I")
2444  AOT_assume ‹Rigid(G)›
2445  AOT_hence ‹□∀z([G]z → □[G]z)›
2446    using "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)] by blast
2447  AOT_hence ‹□□∀z([G]z → □[G]z)› by (metis "S5Basic:6" "≡E"(1))
2448  moreover AOT_have ‹□□∀z([G]z → □[G]z) → □∀x(Numbers(x,G) → □Numbers(x,G))›
2449  proof(rule RM; safe intro!: "→I" GEN)
2450    AOT_modally_strict {
2451      AOT_have act_den: ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2452      fix x
2453      AOT_assume G_nec: ‹□∀z([G]z → □[G]z)›
2454      AOT_hence G_rigid: ‹Rigid(G)›
2455        using "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI", OF "&I"] "cqt:2"
2456        by blast
2457      AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, G)›
2458      AOT_hence ‹[A!]x & G↓ & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2459        using numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
2460      AOT_hence Ax: ‹[A!]x› and ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2461        using "&E" by blast+
2462      AOT_hence ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G› for F
2463        using "∀E"(2) by blast
2464      moreover AOT_have ‹□([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G → □[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› for F
2465        using "approx-nec:3"[unvarify F, OF act_den, THEN "→E", OF "&I",
2466                             OF "actuallyF:2", OF G_rigid].
2467      moreover AOT_have ‹□(x[F] → □x[F])› for F
2468        by (simp add: RN "pre-en-eq:1[1]")
2469      ultimately AOT_have ‹□(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)› for F
2470        using "sc-eq-box-box:5" "→E" "qml:2"[axiom_inst] "&I" by meson
2471      AOT_hence ‹∀F □(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2472        by (rule "∀I")
2473      AOT_hence 1: ‹□∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2474        using BF[THEN "→E"] by fast
2475      AOT_have ‹□G↓›
2476        by (simp add: "ex:2:a")
2477      moreover AOT_have ‹□[A!]x›
2478        using Ax "oa-facts:2" "→E" by blast
2479      ultimately AOT_have ‹□(A!x & G↓)›
2480        by (metis "KBasic:3" "&I" "≡E"(2))
2481      AOT_hence ‹□(A!x & G↓ & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G))›
2482        using 1 "KBasic:3" "&I" "≡E"(2) by fast
2483      AOT_thus ‹□Numbers(x, G)›
2484        by (AOT_subst_def numbers)
2485    }
2486  qed
2487  ultimately AOT_show ‹□∀x(Numbers(x,G) → □Numbers(x,G))›
2488    using "→E" by blast
2489qed

2491AOT_theorem "num-cont:3":
2492  ‹□∀x(Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]) → □Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]))›
2493  by (rule "num-cont:2"[unvarify G, THEN "→E"];
2494      ("cqt:2[lambda]" | rule "actuallyF:2"))

2496AOT_theorem "num-uniq": ‹❙ιx Numbers(x, G)↓›
2497  using "≡E"(2) "A-Exists:2" "RA[2]" "num:2" by blast

2499AOT_define num :: ‹τ ⇒ κ⇩s› (‹#_› [100] 100)
2500  "num-def:1": ‹#G =⇩d⇩f ❙ιx Numbers(x, G)›

2502AOT_theorem "num-def:2": ‹#G↓›
2503  using "num-def:1"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)] "num-uniq" by simp

2505AOT_theorem "num-can:1":
2506  ‹#G = ❙ιx(A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G))›
2507proof -
2508  AOT_have ‹□∀x(Numbers(x,G) ≡ [A!]x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G))›
2509    by (safe intro!: RN GEN "numbers[den]"[THEN "→E"] "cqt:2")
2510  AOT_hence ‹❙ιx Numbers(x, G) = ❙ιx([A!]x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G))›
2511    using "num-uniq" "equiv-desc-eq:3"[THEN "→E", OF "&I"] by auto
2512  thus ?thesis
2513    by (rule "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)[OF "num-def:1", OF "num-uniq"])
2514qed

2516AOT_theorem "num-can:2": ‹#G = ❙ιx(A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2517proof (rule id_trans[OF "num-can:1"]; rule "equiv-desc-eq:2"[THEN "→E"];
2518       safe intro!: "&I" "A-descriptions" GEN "Act-Basic:5"[THEN "≡E"(2)]
2519                    "logic-actual-nec:3"[axiom_inst, THEN "≡E"(2)])
2520  AOT_have act_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F
2521    by "cqt:2"
2522  AOT_have "eq-part:3[terms]": ‹❙⊢⇩□ F ≈⇩E G & F ≈⇩E H → G ≈⇩E H› for F G H
2523    by (metis "&I" "eq-part:2" "eq-part:3" "→I" "&E" "→E")
2524  fix x
2525  {
2526    fix F
2527    AOT_have ‹❙𝒜(F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
2528      by (simp add: "actuallyF:1")
2529    moreover AOT_have ‹❙𝒜((F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]) → ([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2530      by (auto intro!: "RA[2]" "→I" "≡I"
2531               simp: "eq-part:3"[unvarify G, OF act_den, THEN "→E", OF "&I"]
2532                     "eq-part:3[terms]"[unvarify G, OF act_den, THEN "→E", OF "&I"])
2533    ultimately AOT_have ‹❙𝒜([λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G ≡ F ≈⇩E G)›
2534      using "logic-actual-nec:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "≡E"(1), THEN "→E"] by blast
2535
2536    AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G ≡ ❙𝒜F ≈⇩E G›
2537      by (metis "Act-Basic:5" "≡E"(1))
2538    AOT_hence 0: ‹(❙𝒜x[F] ≡ ❙𝒜[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G) ≡ (❙𝒜x[F] ≡ ❙𝒜F ≈⇩E G)›
2539      by (auto intro!: "≡I" "→I" elim: "≡E")
2540    AOT_have ‹❙𝒜(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G) ≡ (❙𝒜x[F] ≡ ❙𝒜[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2541      by (simp add: "Act-Basic:5")
2542    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ (❙𝒜x[F] ≡ ❙𝒜F ≈⇩E G)› using 0.
2543    also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜((x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2544      by (meson "Act-Basic:5" "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:3:a")
2545    finally AOT_have 0: ‹❙𝒜(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G) ≡ ❙𝒜((x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›.
2546  } note 0 = this
2547  AOT_have ‹❙𝒜∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G) ≡ ∀F ❙𝒜(x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)›
2548    using "logic-actual-nec:3" "vdash-properties:1[2]" by blast
2549  also AOT_have ‹… ≡  ∀F ❙𝒜((x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2550    apply (safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" GEN)
2551    using 0 "≡E"(1) "≡E"(2) "rule-ui:3" by blast+
2552  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜(∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2553    using "≡E"(6) "logic-actual-nec:3"[axiom_inst] "oth-class-taut:3:a" by fast
2554  finally AOT_have 0: ‹❙𝒜∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G) ≡ ❙𝒜(∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›.
2555  AOT_have ‹❙𝒜([A!]x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)) ≡
2556            (❙𝒜A!x & ❙𝒜∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G))›
2557    by (simp add: "Act-Basic:2")
2558  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜[A!]x & ❙𝒜(∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2559    using 0 "oth-class-taut:4:f" "→E" by blast
2560  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜(A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›
2561    using "Act-Basic:2" "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:3:a" by blast
2562  finally AOT_show ‹❙𝒜([A!]x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)) ≡
2563                    ❙𝒜([A!]x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≈⇩E G))›.
2564qed

2566AOT_define NaturalCardinal :: ‹τ ⇒ φ› (‹NaturalCardinal'(_')›)
2567  card: ‹NaturalCardinal(x) ≡⇩d⇩f ∃G(x = #G)›
2568
2569AOT_theorem "natcard-nec": ‹NaturalCardinal(x) → □NaturalCardinal(x)›
2570proof(rule "→I")
2571  AOT_assume ‹NaturalCardinal(x)›
2572  AOT_hence ‹∃G(x = #G)› using card[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
2573  then AOT_obtain G where ‹x = #G› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2574  AOT_hence ‹□x = #G› by (metis "id-nec:2" "→E")
2575  AOT_hence ‹∃G □x = #G› by (rule "∃I")
2576  AOT_hence ‹□∃G x = #G› by (metis Buridan "→E")
2577  AOT_thus ‹□NaturalCardinal(x)›
2578    by (AOT_subst_def card)
2579qed

2591  using "equi-rem-thm"

2593                             ‹R |: F ⇩1⇩-⇩1⟷⇩E G› for: R :: ‹<κ×κ>›)

2599AOT_theorem "hume-strict:1":
2600  ‹∃x (Numbers(x, F) & Numbers(x, G)) ≡ F ≈⇩E G›
2601proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
2602  AOT_assume ‹∃x (Numbers(x, F) & Numbers(x, G))›
2603  then AOT_obtain a where ‹Numbers(a, F) & Numbers(a, G)›
2604    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2605  AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E G›
2606    using "num-tran:2" "→E" by blast
2607next
2608  AOT_assume 0: ‹F ≈⇩E G›
2609  moreover AOT_obtain b where num_b_F: ‹Numbers(b, F)›
2610    by (metis "instantiation" "num:1")
2611  moreover AOT_have num_b_G: ‹Numbers(b, G)›
2612    using calculation "num-tran:1"[THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2613  ultimately AOT_have ‹Numbers(b, F) & Numbers(b, G)›
2614    by (safe intro!: "&I")
2615  AOT_thus ‹∃x (Numbers(x, F) & Numbers(x, G))›
2616    by (rule "∃I")
2617qed
2618
2619AOT_theorem "hume-strict:2":
2620  ‹∃x∃y (Numbers(x, F) &
2621         ∀z(Numbers(z,F) → z = x) &
2622         Numbers(y, G) &
2623         ∀z (Numbers(z, G) → z = y) &
2624         x = y) ≡
2625   F ≈⇩E G›
2626proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
2627  AOT_assume ‹∃x∃y (Numbers(x, F) & ∀z(Numbers(z,F) → z = x) &
2628                    Numbers(y, G) & ∀z (Numbers(z, G) → z = y) & x = y)›
2629  then AOT_obtain x where
2630    ‹∃y (Numbers(x, F) & ∀z(Numbers(z,F) → z = x) & Numbers(y, G) &
2631         ∀z (Numbers(z, G) → z = y) & x = y)›
2632    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2633  then AOT_obtain y where
2634    ‹Numbers(x, F) & ∀z(Numbers(z,F) → z = x) & Numbers(y, G) &
2635     ∀z (Numbers(z, G) → z = y) & x = y›
2636    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2637  AOT_hence ‹Numbers(x, F)› and ‹Numbers(y,G)› and ‹x = y›
2638    using "&E" by blast+
2639  AOT_hence ‹Numbers(y, F) & Numbers(y, G)›
2640    using "&I" "rule=E" by fast
2641  AOT_hence ‹∃y (Numbers(y, F) & Numbers(y, G))›
2642    by (rule "∃I")
2643  AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E G›
2644    using "hume-strict:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2645next
2646  AOT_assume ‹F ≈⇩E G›
2647  AOT_hence ‹∃x (Numbers(x, F) & Numbers(x, G))›
2648    using "hume-strict:1"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2649  then AOT_obtain x where ‹Numbers(x, F) & Numbers(x, G)›
2650    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2651  moreover AOT_have ‹∀z (Numbers(z, F) → z = x)›
2652                and ‹∀z (Numbers(z, G) → z = x)›
2653    using calculation
2654    by (auto intro!: GEN "→I" "pre-Hume"[THEN "→E", OF "&I", THEN "≡E"(2),
2655                                         rotated 2, OF "eq-part:1"] dest: "&E")
2656  ultimately AOT_have ‹Numbers(x, F) & ∀z(Numbers(z,F) → z = x) &
2657                       Numbers(x, G) & ∀z (Numbers(z, G) → z = x) & x = x›
2658    by (auto intro!: "&I" "id-eq:1" dest: "&E")
2659  AOT_thus ‹∃x∃y (Numbers(x, F) & ∀z(Numbers(z,F) → z = x) & Numbers(y, G) &
2660                  ∀z (Numbers(z, G) → z = y) & x = y)›
2661    by (auto intro!: "∃I")
2662qed

2664AOT_theorem unotEu: ‹¬∃y[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y›
2665proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
2666  AOT_assume ‹∃y[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y›
2667  then AOT_obtain y where ‹[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y›
2668    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2669  AOT_hence 0: ‹O!y & y ≠⇩E y›
2670    by (rule "β→C"(1))
2671  AOT_hence ‹¬(y =⇩E y)›
2672    using "&E"(2) "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E" by blast
2673  moreover AOT_have ‹y =⇩E y›
2674    by (metis 0[THEN "&E"(1)] "ord=Eequiv:1" "→E")
2675  ultimately AOT_show ‹p & ¬p› for p
2676    by (metis "raa-cor:3")
2677qed

2685AOT_theorem "zero-card": ‹NaturalCardinal(0)›

2690   apply (rule "rule=I:1"; rule "num-def:2"[unvarify G]; "cqt:2")

2693AOT_theorem "eq-num:1":
2694  ‹❙𝒜Numbers(x, G) ≡ Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2695proof -
2696  AOT_have act_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F by "cqt:2"
2697  AOT_have ‹□(∃x(Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])) ≡ G ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2698    using "hume-strict:1"[unvarify G, OF act_den, THEN RN].
2699  AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜(∃x(Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])) ≡ G ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2700    using "nec-imp-act"[THEN "→E"] by fast
2701  AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜(∃x(Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])))›
2702    using "actuallyF:1" "Act-Basic:5" "≡E"(1) "≡E"(2) by fast
2703  AOT_hence ‹∃x ❙𝒜((Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])))›
2704    by (metis "Act-Basic:10" "intro-elim:3:a")
2705  then AOT_obtain a where ‹❙𝒜(Numbers(a, G) & Numbers(a,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z]))›
2706    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2707  AOT_hence act_a_num_G: ‹❙𝒜Numbers(a, G)›
2708     and act_a_num_actG: ‹❙𝒜Numbers(a,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2709    using "Act-Basic:2" "&E" "≡E"(1) by blast+
2710  AOT_hence num_a_act_g: ‹Numbers(a, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2711    using "num-cont:2"[unvarify G, OF act_den, THEN "→E", OF "actuallyF:2",
2712                       THEN CBF[THEN "→E"], THEN "∀E"(2)]
2713    by (metis "≡E"(1) "sc-eq-fur:2" "vdash-properties:6")
2714  AOT_have 0: ‹❙⊢⇩□ Numbers(x, G) & Numbers(y, G) → x = y› for y
2715    using "pre-Hume"[THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(2), rotated, OF "eq-part:1"]
2716          "→I" by blast
2717  show ?thesis
2718  proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
2719    AOT_assume ‹❙𝒜Numbers(x, G)›
2720    AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜x = a›
2721      using 0[THEN "RA[2]", THEN "act-cond"[THEN "→E"], THEN "→E",
2722              OF "Act-Basic:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)], OF "&I"]
2723            act_a_num_G by blast
2724    AOT_hence ‹x = a› by (metis "id-act:1" "≡E"(2))
2725    AOT_hence ‹a = x› using id_sym by auto
2726    AOT_thus ‹Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2727      using "rule=E" num_a_act_g by fast
2728  next
2729    AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2730    AOT_hence ‹a = x›
2731      using "pre-Hume"[unvarify G H, THEN "→E", OF act_den, OF act_den, OF "&I",
2732                       OF num_a_act_g, THEN "≡E"(2)]
2733            "eq-part:1"[unvarify F, OF act_den] by blast
2734    AOT_thus ‹❙𝒜Numbers(x, G)›
2735      using act_a_num_G "rule=E" by fast
2736  qed
2737qed
2738
2739AOT_theorem "eq-num:2": ‹Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[G]z]) ≡ x = #G›
2740proof -
2741  AOT_have 0: ‹❙⊢⇩□ x = ❙ιx Numbers(x, G) ≡ ∀y (Numbers(y, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]) ≡ y = x)› for x
2742    by (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])› ‹❙𝒜Numbers(x, G)› for: x)
2743       (auto simp: "eq-num:1" descriptions[axiom_inst])
2744  AOT_have ‹#G = ❙ιx Numbers(x, G) ≡ ∀y (Numbers(y, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]) ≡ y = #G)›
2745    using 0[unvarify x, OF "num-def:2"].
2746  moreover AOT_have ‹#G = ❙ιx Numbers(x, G)›
2747    using "num-def:1" "num-uniq" "rule-id-df:1" by blast
2748  ultimately AOT_have ‹∀y (Numbers(y, [λz ❙𝒜[G]z]) ≡ y = #G)›
2749    using "≡E" by blast
2750  thus ?thesis using "∀E"(2) by blast
2751qed
2752
2753AOT_theorem "eq-num:3": ‹Numbers(#G, [λy ❙𝒜[G]y])›
2754proof -
2755  AOT_have ‹#G = #G›
2756    by (simp add: "rule=I:1" "num-def:2")
2757  thus ?thesis
2758    using "eq-num:2"[unvarify x, OF "num-def:2", THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2759qed

2761AOT_theorem "eq-num:4":
2762  ‹A!#G & ∀F (#G[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[G]z])›
2763  by (auto intro!: "&I" "eq-num:3"[THEN numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"],
2764                                   THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
2765                   "eq-num:3"[THEN numbers[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"], THEN "&E"(2)])
2766
2767AOT_theorem "eq-num:5": ‹#G[G]›
2768  by (auto intro!: "eq-num:4"[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "≡E"(2)]
2769                   "eq-part:1"[unvarify F] simp: "cqt:2")

2771AOT_theorem "eq-num:6": ‹Numbers(x, G) → NaturalCardinal(x)›
2772proof(rule "→I")
2773  AOT_have act_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F
2774    by "cqt:2"
2775  AOT_obtain F where ‹Rigidifies(F, G)›
2776    by (metis "instantiation" "rigid-der:3")
2777  AOT_hence θ: ‹Rigid(F)› and ‹∀x([F]x ≡ [G]x)›
2778    using "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)]
2779          "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(1)]
2780    by blast+
2781  AOT_hence ‹F ≡⇩E G›
2782    by (auto intro!: eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2" GEN "→I" elim: "∀E"(2))
2783  moreover AOT_assume ‹Numbers(x, G)›
2784  ultimately AOT_have ‹Numbers(x, F)›
2785    using "num-tran:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2786  moreover AOT_have ‹F ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]›
2787    using θ "approx-nec:1" "→E" by blast
2788  ultimately AOT_have ‹Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
2789    using "num-tran:1"[unvarify H, OF act_den, THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2790  AOT_hence ‹x = #F›
2791    using "eq-num:2"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
2792  AOT_hence ‹∃F x = #F›
2793    by (rule "∃I")
2794  AOT_thus ‹NaturalCardinal(x)›
2795    using card[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] by blast
2796qed

2798AOT_theorem "eq-df-num": ‹∃G (x = #G) ≡ ∃G (Numbers(x,G))›
2799proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
2800  AOT_assume ‹∃G (x = #G)›
2801  then AOT_obtain P where ‹x = #P›
2802    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2803  AOT_hence ‹Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[P]z])›
2804    using "eq-num:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2805  moreover AOT_have ‹[λz ❙𝒜[P]z]↓› by "cqt:2"
2806  ultimately AOT_show ‹∃G(Numbers(x,G))› by (rule "∃I")
2807next
2808  AOT_assume ‹∃G (Numbers(x,G))›
2809  then AOT_obtain Q where ‹Numbers(x,Q)›
2810    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2811  AOT_hence ‹NaturalCardinal(x)›
2812    using "eq-num:6"[THEN "→E"] by blast
2813  AOT_thus ‹∃G (x = #G)›
2814    using card[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
2815qed

2817AOT_theorem "card-en": ‹NaturalCardinal(x) → ∀F(x[F] ≡ x = #F)›
2818proof(rule "→I"; rule GEN)
2819  AOT_have act_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F by "cqt:2"
2820  fix F
2821  AOT_assume ‹NaturalCardinal(x)›
2822  AOT_hence ‹∃F x = #F›
2823    using card[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
2824  then AOT_obtain P where x_def: ‹x = #P›
2825    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
2826  AOT_hence num_x_act_P: ‹Numbers(x,[λz ❙𝒜[P]z])›
2827    using "eq-num:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
2828  AOT_have ‹#P[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[P]z]›
2829    using "eq-num:4"[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)] by blast
2830  AOT_hence ‹x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[P]z]›
2831    using x_def[symmetric] "rule=E" by fast
2832  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ Numbers(x, [λz ❙𝒜[F]z])›
2833    using "num-tran:1"[unvarify G H, OF act_den, OF act_den]
2834    using "num-tran:2"[unvarify G H, OF act_den, OF act_den]
2835    by (metis "&I" "deduction-theorem" "≡I" "≡E"(2) num_x_act_P)
2836  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ x = #F›
2837    using "eq-num:2" by blast
2838  finally AOT_show ‹x[F] ≡ x = #F›.
2839qed

2841AOT_theorem "0F:1": ‹¬∃u [F]u ≡ Numbers(0, F)›
2842proof -
2843  AOT_have unotEu_act_ord: ‹¬∃v[λx O!x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]v›
2844  proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
2845    AOT_assume ‹∃v[λx O!x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]v›
2846    then AOT_obtain y where ‹[λx O!x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]y›
2847      using "∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
2848    AOT_hence 0: ‹O!y & ❙𝒜y ≠⇩E y›
2849      by (rule "β→C"(1))
2850    AOT_have ‹❙𝒜¬(y =⇩E y)›
2851      apply (AOT_subst  ‹¬(y =⇩E y)› ‹y ≠⇩E y›)
2852       apply (meson "≡E"(2) "Commutativity of ≡" "thm-neg=E")
2853      by (fact 0[THEN "&E"(2)])
2854    AOT_hence ‹¬(y =⇩E y)›
2855      by (metis "¬¬I" "Act-Sub:1" "id-act2:1" "≡E"(4))
2856    moreover AOT_have ‹y =⇩E y›
2857      by (metis 0[THEN "&E"(1)] "ord=Eequiv:1" "→E")
2858    ultimately AOT_show ‹p & ¬p› for p
2859      by (metis "raa-cor:3")
2860  qed
2861  AOT_have ‹Numbers(0, [λy ❙𝒜[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y])›
2862    apply (rule "=⇩d⇩fI"(2)[OF "zero:1"])
2863     apply (rule "num-def:2"[unvarify G]; "cqt:2")
2864    apply (rule "eq-num:3"[unvarify G])
2865    by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2866  AOT_hence numbers0: ‹Numbers(0, [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x])›
2867  proof (rule "num-tran:3"[unvarify x G H, THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(1), rotated 4])
2868    AOT_show ‹[λy ❙𝒜[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y] ≡⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]›
2869    proof (safe intro!: eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" Ordinary.GEN "→I" "cqt:2")
2870      fix u
2871      AOT_have ‹[λy ❙𝒜[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y]u ≡ ❙𝒜[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]u›
2872        by (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
2873      also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜(O!u & u ≠⇩E u)›
2874        apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]u› ‹O!u & u ≠⇩E u›)
2875         apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
2876        by (simp add: "oth-class-taut:3:a")
2877      also AOT_have ‹… ≡ (❙𝒜O!u & ❙𝒜u ≠⇩E u)›
2878        by (simp add: "Act-Basic:2")
2879      also AOT_have ‹… ≡ (O!u & ❙𝒜u ≠⇩E u)›
2880        by (metis Ordinary.ψ "&I" "&E"(2) "→I" "≡I" "≡E"(1) "oa-facts:7")
2881      also AOT_have ‹… ≡ [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]u›
2882        by (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", symmetric]; "cqt:2[lambda]")
2883      finally AOT_show ‹[λy ❙𝒜[λx O!x & x ≠⇩E x]y]u ≡ [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]u›.
2884    qed
2885  qed(fact "zero:2" | "cqt:2")+
2886  show ?thesis
2887  proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
2888    AOT_assume ‹¬∃u [F]u›
2889    moreover AOT_have ‹¬∃v [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]v›
2890      using unotEu_act_ord.
2891    ultimately AOT_have 0: ‹F ≈⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]›
2892      by (rule "empty-approx:1"[unvarify H, THEN "→E", rotated, OF "&I"]) "cqt:2"
2893    AOT_thus ‹Numbers(0, F)›
2894      by (rule "num-tran:1"[unvarify x H, THEN "→E",
2895                            THEN "≡E"(2), rotated, rotated])
2896         (fact "zero:2" numbers0 | "cqt:2[lambda]")+
2897  next
2898    AOT_assume ‹Numbers(0, F)›
2899    AOT_hence 1: ‹F ≈⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]›
2900      by (rule "num-tran:2"[unvarify x H, THEN "→E", rotated 2, OF "&I"])
2901         (fact numbers0 "zero:2" | "cqt:2[lambda]")+
2902    AOT_show ‹¬∃u [F]u›
2903    proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
2904      AOT_have 0: ‹[λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
2905      AOT_assume ‹∃u [F]u›
2906      AOT_hence ‹¬(F ≈⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x])›
2907        by (rule "empty-approx:2"[unvarify H, OF 0, THEN "→E", OF "&I"])
2908           (rule unotEu_act_ord)
2909      AOT_thus ‹F ≈⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x] & ¬(F ≈⇩E [λx [O!]x & ❙𝒜x ≠⇩E x])› 
2910        using 1 "&I" by blast
2911    qed
2912  qed
2913qed

3045        by (AOT_subst ‹[λx w ⊨ [F]x]x› ‹w ⊨ [F]x›;
3046            safe intro!: "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"] "w-rel:1"[THEN "→E"]) "cqt:2"
3047      AOT_hence ‹O!x & ❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]x›
3048        using ord_x "&I" by blast
3049      AOT_hence ‹∃x (O!x & ❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]x)›
3050        using "∃I" by fast
3051      AOT_thus ‹∃u (❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]u) & ¬∃u ❙𝒜[λx w ⊨ [F]x]u›
3052        using 0 "&I" by blast
3053    qed
3054    AOT_thus ‹w ⊨ ¬∃u[F]u›
3055      using "coherent:1"[unvarify p, OF "log-prop-prop:2", THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
3056  qed
3057qed

3059AOT_act_theorem "zero=:1":
3060  ‹NaturalCardinal(x) → ∀F (x[F] ≡ Numbers(x, F))›
3061proof(safe intro!: "→I" GEN)
3062  fix F
3063  AOT_assume ‹NaturalCardinal(x)›
3064  AOT_hence ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ x = #F)›
3065    by (metis "card-en" "→E")
3066  AOT_hence 1: ‹x[F] ≡ x = #F›
3067    using "∀E"(2) by blast
3068  AOT_have 2: ‹x[F] ≡ x = ❙ιy(Numbers(y, F))›
3069    by (rule "num-def:1"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fE"(1)])
3070       (auto simp: 1 "num-uniq")
3071  AOT_have ‹x = ❙ιy(Numbers(y, F)) → Numbers(x, F)›
3072    using "y-in:1" by blast
3073  moreover AOT_have ‹Numbers(x, F) → x = ❙ιy(Numbers(y, F))›
3074  proof(rule "→I")
3075    AOT_assume 1: ‹Numbers(x, F)›
3076    moreover AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹∀y (Numbers(y, F) → y = z)›
3077      using "num:2"[THEN "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"]] "∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
3078    ultimately AOT_have ‹x = z›
3079      using "∀E"(2) "→E" by blast
3080    AOT_hence ‹∀y (Numbers(y, F) → y = x)›
3081      using z_prop "rule=E" id_sym by fast
3082    AOT_thus ‹x = ❙ιy(Numbers(y,F))›
3083      by (rule hintikka[THEN "≡E"(2), OF "&I", rotated])
3084         (fact 1)
3085  qed
3086  ultimately AOT_have ‹x = ❙ιy(Numbers(y, F)) ≡ Numbers(x, F)›
3087    by (metis "≡I")
3088  AOT_thus ‹x[F] ≡ Numbers(x, F)›
3089    using 2 by (metis "≡E"(5))
3090qed

3267       (auto simp: 1 "id-nec:2" "≡I" "qml:2"[axiom_inst])

3271    using "CBF"[THEN "→E"] by fast

3273    using tuple_forall[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast

3275    using "∀E"(2) by blast

3279                     □(([R]xz & [R]yz) → □([R]xz & [R]yz))› for x y z

3388  ‹x =⇩ℛ y → (InDomainOf(x, ℛ) & InDomainOf(y, ℛ))›
3389proof(rule "→I")
3390  AOT_assume ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
3391  AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz)›
3392    using "id-R-thm:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by simp
3393  then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹[ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz›
3394    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3395  AOT_show ‹InDomainOf(x, ℛ) & InDomainOf(y, ℛ)›
3396  proof (safe intro!: "&I" "df-1-1:5"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
3397    AOT_show ‹∃y [ℛ]xy›
3398      using z_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "∃I" by fast
3399  next
3400    AOT_show ‹∃z [ℛ]yz›
3401      using z_prop[THEN "&E"(2)] "∃I" by fast
3402  qed
3403qed

3405AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:3": ‹x =⇩ℛ y → x = y›
3406proof(rule "→I")
3407  AOT_assume ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
3408  AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz)›
3409    using "id-R-thm:1"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by simp
3410  then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹[ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz›
3411    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3412  AOT_thus ‹x = y›
3413    using "df-1-1:3"[THEN "→E", OF RigidOneToOneRelation.ψ,
3414                     THEN "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"],
3415                     THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "df-1-1:1"], THEN "&E"(2),
3416                     THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2),
3417                     THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"]
3418     by blast
3419qed

3421AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:4":
3422  ‹(InDomainOf(x, ℛ) ∨ InDomainOf(y, ℛ)) → (x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y)›
3423proof (rule "→I")
3424  AOT_assume ‹InDomainOf(x, ℛ) ∨ InDomainOf(y, ℛ)›
3425  moreover {
3426    AOT_assume ‹InDomainOf(x, ℛ)›
3427    AOT_hence ‹∃z [ℛ]xz›
3428      by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "df-1-1:5")
3429    then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹[ℛ]xz›
3430      using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3431    AOT_have ‹x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y›
3432    proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" "id-R-thm:3"[THEN "→E"])
3433      AOT_assume ‹x = y›
3434      AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]yz›
3435        using z_prop "rule=E" by fast
3436      AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz›
3437        using z_prop "&I" by blast
3438      AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz)›
3439        by (rule "∃I")
3440      AOT_thus ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
3441        using "id-R-thm:1" "≡E"(2) by blast
3442    qed
3443  }
3444  moreover {
3445    AOT_assume ‹InDomainOf(y, ℛ)›
3446    AOT_hence ‹∃z [ℛ]yz›
3447      by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "df-1-1:5")
3448    then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹[ℛ]yz›
3449      using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3450    AOT_have ‹x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y›
3451    proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" "id-R-thm:3"[THEN "→E"])
3452      AOT_assume ‹x = y›
3453      AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]xz›
3454        using z_prop "rule=E" id_sym by fast
3455      AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz›
3456        using z_prop "&I" by blast
3457      AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]yz)›
3458        by (rule "∃I")
3459      AOT_thus ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
3460        using "id-R-thm:1" "≡E"(2) by blast
3461    qed
3462  }
3463  ultimately AOT_show ‹x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y›
3464    by (metis "∨E"(2) "raa-cor:1")
3465qed

3467AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:5": ‹InDomainOf(x, ℛ) → x =⇩ℛ x›
3468proof (rule "→I")
3469  AOT_assume ‹InDomainOf(x, ℛ)›
3470  AOT_hence ‹∃z [ℛ]xz›
3471    by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "df-1-1:5")
3472  then AOT_obtain z where z_prop: ‹[ℛ]xz›
3473    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3474  AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]xz & [ℛ]xz›
3475    using "&I" by blast
3476  AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]xz & [ℛ]xz)›
3477    using "∃I" by fast
3478  AOT_thus ‹x =⇩ℛ x›
3479    using "id-R-thm:1" "≡E"(2) by blast
3480qed

3482AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:6": ‹x =⇩ℛ y → y =⇩ℛ x›
3483proof(rule "→I")
3484  AOT_assume 0: ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
3485  AOT_hence 1: ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ) & InDomainOf(y,ℛ)›
3486    using "id-R-thm:2"[THEN "→E"] by blast
3487  AOT_hence ‹x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y›
3488    using "id-R-thm:4"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(1)] "&E" by blast
3489  AOT_hence ‹x = y›
3490    using 0 by (metis "≡E"(1))
3491  AOT_hence ‹y = x›
3492    using id_sym by blast
3493  moreover AOT_have ‹y =⇩ℛ x ≡ y = x›
3494    using "id-R-thm:4"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(2)] 1 "&E" by blast
3495  ultimately AOT_show ‹y =⇩ℛ x›
3496    by (metis "≡E"(2))
3497qed

3499AOT_theorem "id-R-thm:7": ‹x =⇩ℛ y & y =⇩ℛ z → x =⇩ℛ z›
3500proof (rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
3501  AOT_assume 0: ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
3502  AOT_hence 1: ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ) & InDomainOf(y,ℛ)›
3503    using "id-R-thm:2"[THEN "→E"] by blast
3504  AOT_hence ‹x =⇩ℛ y ≡ x = y›
3505    using "id-R-thm:4"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(1)] "&E" by blast
3506  AOT_hence x_eq_y: ‹x = y›
3507    using 0 by (metis "≡E"(1))
3508  AOT_assume 2: ‹y =⇩ℛ z›
3509  AOT_hence 3: ‹InDomainOf(y,ℛ) & InDomainOf(z,ℛ)›
3510    using "id-R-thm:2"[THEN "→E"] by blast
3511  AOT_hence ‹y =⇩ℛ z ≡ y = z›
3512    using "id-R-thm:4"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(1)] "&E" by blast
3513  AOT_hence ‹y = z›
3514    using 2 by (metis "≡E"(1))
3515  AOT_hence x_eq_z: ‹x = z›
3516    using x_eq_y id_trans by blast
3517  AOT_have ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ) & InDomainOf(z,ℛ)›
3518    using 1 3 "&I" "&E" by meson
3519  AOT_hence ‹x =⇩ℛ z ≡ x = z›
3520    using "id-R-thm:4"[THEN "→E", OF "∨I"(1)] "&E" by blast
3521  AOT_thus ‹x =⇩ℛ z›
3522    using x_eq_z "≡E"(2) by blast
3523qed

3525AOT_define WeakAncestral :: ‹Π ⇒ Π› (‹_⇧+›)
3526  "w-ances-df": ‹[ℛ]⇧+ =⇩d⇩f [λxy [ℛ]⇧*xy ∨ x =⇩ℛ y]›
3527
3528AOT_theorem "w-ances-df[den1]": ‹[λxy [Π]⇧*xy ∨ x =⇩Π y]↓›
3529  by "cqt:2"
3530AOT_theorem "w-ances-df[den2]": ‹[Π]⇧+↓›
3531  using "w-ances-df[den1]" "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)[OF "w-ances-df"] by blast
3532
3533AOT_theorem "w-ances": ‹[ℛ]⇧+xy ≡ ([ℛ]⇧*xy ∨ x =⇩ℛ y)›
3534proof -
3535  AOT_have 0: ‹[λxy [ℛ⇧*]xy ∨ x =⇩ℛ y]↓›
3536    by "cqt:2"
3537  AOT_have 1: ‹«(AOT_term_of_var x,AOT_term_of_var y)»↓›
3538    by (simp add: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")
3539  have 2: ‹«[λμ⇩1...μ⇩n [ℛ⇧*]μ⇩1...μ⇩n ∨ [(=⇩ℛ)]μ⇩1...μ⇩n]xy» =
3540           «[λxy [ℛ⇧*]xy ∨ [(=⇩ℛ)]xy]xy»›
3541    by (simp add: cond_case_prod_eta)
3542  show ?thesis
3543    apply (rule "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)[OF "w-ances-df"])
3544     apply (fact "w-ances-df[den1]")
3545    using "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF 0, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n,
3546                        where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified, OF 1] 2 by simp
3547qed

3554  AOT_thus ‹[ℛ]⇧+xy›
3555    using "w-ances"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "∨I" by blast
3556qed

3576      using 0 "rule=E" by blast
3577  }

3580qed

3596                              THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] by blast
3597      AOT_thus ‹[F]z›
3598        using "hered:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", OF 0[THEN "&E"(2)], THEN "&E"(2)]
3599              "∀E"(2) "→E" Ryz by blast
3600    qed
3601  }
3602  moreover {

3604    AOT_hence ‹x = y›
3605      using "id-R-thm:3"[THEN "→E"] by blast

3607      using Ryz "rule=E" id_sym by fast

3609      by (metis "anc-her:1"[THEN "→E"])

3613qed

3694AOT_theorem "w-ances-her:7": ‹[ℛ]⇧*xy → ∃z([ℛ]⇧+xz & [ℛ]zy)›
3695proof(rule "→I")
3696  AOT_assume 0: ‹[ℛ]⇧*xy›
3697  AOT_have 1: ‹∀z ([ℛ]xz → [Π]z) & Hereditary(Π,ℛ) → [Π]y› if ‹Π↓› for Π
3698    using ances[THEN "≡E"(1), THEN "∀E"(1), OF 0] that by blast
3699  AOT_have ‹[λy ∃z([ℛ]⇧+xz & [ℛ]zy)]y›
3700  proof (rule 1[THEN "→E"]; "cqt:2[lambda]"?;
3701         safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" "hered:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "cqt:2")
3702    fix z
3703    AOT_assume 0: ‹[ℛ]xz›
3704    AOT_hence ‹∃z [ℛ]xz› by (rule "∃I")
3705    AOT_hence ‹InDomainOf(x, ℛ)› by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fI" "df-1-1:5")
3706    AOT_hence ‹x =⇩ℛ x› by (metis "id-R-thm:5" "→E")
3707    AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]⇧+xx› by (metis "∨I"(2) "≡E"(2) "w-ances")
3708    AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]⇧+xx & [ℛ]xz› using 0 "&I" by blast
3709    AOT_hence ‹∃y ([ℛ]⇧+xy & [ℛ]yz)› by (rule "∃I")
3710    AOT_thus ‹[λy ∃z ([ℛ]⇧+xz & [ℛ]zy)]z›
3711      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
3712  next
3713    fix x' y
3714    AOT_assume Rx'y: ‹[ℛ]x'y›
3715    AOT_assume ‹[λy ∃z ([ℛ]⇧+xz & [ℛ]zy)]x'›
3716    AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]⇧+xz & [ℛ]zx')›
3717      using "β→C"(1) by blast
3718    then AOT_obtain c where c_prop: ‹[ℛ]⇧+xc & [ℛ]cx'›
3719      using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3720    AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]⇧*xx'›
3721      by (meson Rx'y "anc-her:1" "anc-her:6" Adjunction "→E" "w-ances-her:3")
3722    AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]⇧*xx' ∨ x =⇩ℛ x'› by (rule "∨I")
3723    AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]⇧+xx'› by (metis "≡E"(2) "w-ances")
3724    AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]⇧+xx' & [ℛ]x'y› using Rx'y by (metis "&I")
3725    AOT_hence ‹∃z ([ℛ]⇧+xz & [ℛ]zy)› by (rule "∃I")
3726    AOT_thus ‹[λy ∃z ([ℛ]⇧+xz & [ℛ]zy)]y›
3727      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
3728  qed
3729  AOT_thus ‹∃z([ℛ]⇧+xz & [ℛ]zy)›
3730    using "β→C"(1) by fast
3731qed

3750AOT_theorem "1-1-R:2": ‹[ℛ]xy → (¬[ℛ]⇧*xx → ¬[ℛ]⇧*yy)›
3751proof(rule "→I"; rule "useful-tautologies:5"[THEN "→E"]; rule "→I")
3752  AOT_assume 0: ‹[ℛ]xy›
3753  moreover AOT_assume ‹[ℛ]⇧*yy›
3754  ultimately AOT_have ‹[ℛ]⇧+yx›
3755    using "1-1-R:1"[THEN "→E", OF "&I"] by blast
3756  AOT_thus ‹[ℛ]⇧*xx›
3757    using 0 by (metis "&I" "→E" "w-ances-her:5")
3758qed

3760AOT_theorem "1-1-R:3": ‹¬[ℛ]⇧*xx → ([ℛ]⇧+xy → ¬[ℛ]⇧*yy)›
3761proof(safe intro!: "→I")
3762  AOT_have 0: ‹[λz ¬[ℛ]⇧*zz]↓› by "cqt:2"
3763  AOT_assume 1: ‹¬[ℛ]⇧*xx›
3764  AOT_assume 2: ‹[ℛ]⇧+xy›
3765  AOT_have ‹[λz ¬[ℛ]⇧*zz]y›
3766  proof(rule "w-ances-her:2"[unvarify F, OF 0, THEN "→E"];
3767        safe intro!: "&I" "hered:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "cqt:2" GEN "→I")
3768    AOT_show  ‹[λz ¬[ℛ]⇧*zz]x›
3769      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" simp: 1)
3770  next
3771    AOT_show ‹[ℛ]⇧+xy› by (fact 2)
3772  next
3773    fix x y
3774    AOT_assume ‹[λz ¬[ℛ⇧*]zz]x›
3775    AOT_hence ‹¬[ℛ]⇧*xx› by (rule "β→C"(1))
3776    moreover AOT_assume ‹[ℛ]xy›
3777    ultimately AOT_have ‹¬[ℛ]⇧*yy›
3778      using "1-1-R:2"[THEN "→E", THEN "→E"] by blast
3779    AOT_thus ‹[λz ¬[ℛ⇧*]zz]y›
3780      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
3781  qed
3782  AOT_thus ‹¬[ℛ]⇧*yy›
3783    using "β→C"(1) by blast
3784qed

3786AOT_theorem "1-1-R:4": ‹[ℛ]⇧*xy → InDomainOf(x,ℛ)›
3787proof(rule "→I"; rule "df-1-1:5"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
3788  AOT_assume 1: ‹[ℛ]⇧*xy›
3789  AOT_have ‹[λz [ℛ⇧*]xz → ∃y [ℛ]xy]y›
3790  proof (safe intro!: "anc-her:2"[unvarify F, THEN "→E"];
3791         safe intro!: "cqt:2" "&I" GEN "→I" "hered:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
3792    AOT_show ‹[ℛ]⇧*xy› by (fact 1)
3793  next
3794    fix z
3795    AOT_assume ‹[ℛ]xz›
3796    AOT_thus ‹[λz [ℛ⇧*]xz → ∃y [ℛ]xy]z›
3797      by (safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
3798         (meson "→I" "existential:2[const_var]")
3799  next
3800    fix x' y
3801    AOT_assume Rx'y: ‹[ℛ]x'y›
3802    AOT_assume ‹[λz [ℛ⇧*]xz → ∃y [ℛ]xy]x'›
3803    AOT_hence 0: ‹[ℛ⇧*]xx' → ∃y [ℛ]xy› by (rule "β→C"(1))
3804    AOT_have 1: ‹[ℛ⇧*]xy → ∃y [ℛ]xy›
3805    proof(rule "→I")
3806      AOT_assume ‹[ℛ]⇧*xy›
3807      AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]⇧+xx'› by (metis Rx'y "&I" "1-1-R:1" "→E")
3808      AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]⇧*xx' ∨ x =⇩ℛ x'› by (metis "≡E"(1) "w-ances")
3809      moreover {
3810        AOT_assume ‹[ℛ]⇧*xx'›
3811        AOT_hence ‹∃y [ℛ]xy› using 0 by (metis "→E")
3812      }
3813      moreover {
3814        AOT_assume ‹x =⇩ℛ x'›
3815        AOT_hence ‹x = x'› by (metis "id-R-thm:3" "→E")
3816        AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]xy› using Rx'y "rule=E" id_sym by fast
3817        AOT_hence ‹∃y [ℛ]xy› by (rule "∃I")
3818      }
3819      ultimately AOT_show ‹∃y [ℛ]xy›
3820        by (metis "∨E"(3) "reductio-aa:1")
3821    qed
3822    AOT_show ‹[λz [ℛ⇧*]xz → ∃y [ℛ]xy]y›
3823      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" 1)
3824  qed
3825  AOT_hence ‹[ℛ⇧*]xy → ∃y [ℛ]xy› by (rule "β→C"(1))
3826  AOT_thus ‹∃y [ℛ]xy› using 1 "→E" by blast
3827qed

3829AOT_theorem "1-1-R:5": ‹[ℛ]⇧+xy → InDomainOf(x,ℛ)›
3830proof (rule "→I")
3831  AOT_assume ‹[ℛ]⇧+xy›
3832  AOT_hence ‹[ℛ]⇧*xy ∨ x =⇩ℛ y›
3833    by (metis "≡E"(1) "w-ances")
3834  moreover {
3835    AOT_assume ‹[ℛ]⇧*xy›
3836    AOT_hence ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ)›
3837      using "1-1-R:4" "→E" by blast
3838  }
3839  moreover {
3840    AOT_assume ‹x =⇩ℛ y›
3841    AOT_hence ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ)›
3842      by (metis "Conjunction Simplification"(1) "id-R-thm:2" "→E")
3843  }
3844  ultimately AOT_show ‹InDomainOf(x,ℛ)›
3845    by (metis "∨E"(3) "reductio-aa:1")
3846qed

3848AOT_theorem "pre-ind":
3849  ‹([F]z & ∀x∀y(([ℛ]⇧+zx & [ℛ]⇧+zy) → ([ℛ]xy → ([F]x → [F]y)))) →
3850   ∀x ([ℛ]⇧+zx → [F]x)›
3851proof(safe intro!: "→I" GEN)
3852  AOT_have den: ‹[λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy]↓› by "cqt:2"
3853  fix x
3854  AOT_assume θ: ‹[F]z & ∀x∀y(([ℛ]⇧+zx & [ℛ]⇧+zy) → ([ℛ]xy → ([F]x → [F]y)))›
3855  AOT_assume 0: ‹[ℛ]⇧+zx›
3856
3857  AOT_have ‹[λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy]x›
3858  proof (rule "w-ances-her:2"[unvarify F, OF den, THEN "→E"]; safe intro!: "&I")
3859    AOT_show ‹[λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy]z›
3860    proof (safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I")
3861      AOT_show ‹[F]z› using θ "&E" by blast
3862    next
3863      AOT_show ‹[ℛ]⇧+zz›
3864        by (rule "w-ances"[THEN "≡E"(2), OF "∨I"(2)])
3865           (meson "0" "id-R-thm:5" "1-1-R:5" "→E")
3866    qed
3867  next
3868    AOT_show ‹[ℛ]⇧+zx› by (fact 0)
3869  next
3870    AOT_show ‹Hereditary([λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy],ℛ)›
3871    proof (safe intro!: "hered:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2" GEN "→I")
3872      fix x' y
3873      AOT_assume 1: ‹[ℛ]x'y›
3874      AOT_assume ‹[λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy]x'›
3875      AOT_hence 2: ‹[F]x' & [ℛ]⇧+zx'› by (rule "β→C"(1))
3876      AOT_have ‹[ℛ]⇧*zy› using 1 2[THEN "&E"(2)]
3877        by (metis Adjunction "modus-tollens:1" "reductio-aa:1" "w-ances-her:3")
3878      AOT_hence 3: ‹[ℛ]⇧+zy› by (metis "∨I"(1) "≡E"(2) "w-ances")
3879      AOT_show ‹[λy [F]y & [ℛ]⇧+zy]y›
3880      proof (safe intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "&I" 3)
3881        AOT_show ‹[F]y›
3882        proof (rule θ[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2),
3883                      THEN "→E", THEN "→E", THEN "→E"])
3884          AOT_show ‹[ℛ]⇧+zx' & [ℛ]⇧+zy›
3885            using 2 3 "&E" "&I" by blast
3886        next
3887          AOT_show ‹[ℛ]x'y› by (fact 1)
3888        next
3889          AOT_show ‹[F]x'› using 2 "&E" by blast
3890        qed
3891      qed
3892    qed
3893  qed
3894  AOT_thus ‹[F]x› using "β→C"(1) "&E"(1) by fast
3895qed

3897text‹This is not part of PLM, but a consequence of extended relation comprehension
3898     and can be used to @{emph ‹derive›} the predecessor axiom.›

3900AOT_theorem numbers_prop_den: ‹[λx Numbers(x,G)]↓›
3901proof (rule "safe-ext"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E", OF "&I"])
3902  AOT_show ‹[λx A!x & [λx ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)]x]↓›
3903    by "cqt:2"
3904next
3905  AOT_have 0: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λx ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)]↓›
3906  proof(safe intro!: Comprehension_3[THEN "→E"] "→I" RN GEN)
3907      AOT_modally_strict {
3908        fix F H
3909        AOT_assume ‹□H ≡⇩E F›
3910        AOT_hence ‹□∀u ([H]u ≡ [F]u)›
3911          by (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹∀u ([H]u ≡ [F]u)› ‹H ≡⇩E F›)
3912              (safe intro!: "eqE"[THEN "≡Df", THEN "≡S"(1), OF "&I"] "cqt:2")
3913        AOT_hence ‹∀u □([H]u ≡ [F]u)›
3914          by (metis "Ordinary.res-var-bound-reas[CBF]" "→E")
3915        AOT_hence ‹□([H]u ≡ [F]u)› for u
3916          using "Ordinary.∀E" by fast
3917        AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜([H]u ≡ [F]u)› for u
3918          by (metis "nec-imp-act" "→E")
3919        AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜([F]u ≡ [H]u)› for u
3920          by (metis "Act-Basic:5" "Commutativity of ≡" "intro-elim:3:b")
3921        AOT_hence ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≡⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[H]z]›
3922          by (safe intro!: "eqE"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "cqt:2" Ordinary.GEN;
3923              AOT_subst ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u› ‹❙𝒜[F]u› for: u F)
3924             (auto intro!: "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"] "cqt:2"
3925                           "Act-Basic:5"[THEN "≡E"(1)])
3926        AOT_hence ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E [λz ❙𝒜[H]z]›
3927          by (safe intro!: "apE-eqE:1"[unvarify F G, THEN "→E"] "cqt:2")
3928        AOT_thus ‹[λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[H]z] ≈⇩E G›
3929          using "≡I" "eq-part:2[terms]" "eq-part:3[terms]" "→E" "→I"
3930          by metis
3931      }
3932  qed
3933  AOT_show ‹□∀x (A!x & [λx ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)]x ≡ Numbers(x,G))›
3934  proof (safe intro!: RN GEN)
3935    AOT_modally_strict {
3936      fix x
3937      AOT_show ‹A!x & [λx ∀F (x[F] ≡ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z] ≈⇩E G)]x ≡ Numbers(x,G)›
3938        by (AOT_subst_def numbers; AOT_subst_thm "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF 0])
3939           (auto intro!: "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF 0] "≡I" "→I" "&I" "cqt:2"
3940                   dest: "&E")
3941    }
3942  qed
3943qed

3945AOT_theorem pred: ‹[λxy ∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))]↓›
3946proof -
3947  AOT_have prod_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ «(AOT_term_of_var x⇩1,AOT_term_of_var x⇩2)»↓›
3948    for x⇩1 x⇩2 :: ‹κ AOT_var›
3949    by (simp add: "&I" "ex:1:a" prod_denotesI "rule-ui:3")
3950  AOT_have proj1_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λxy [F]x]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
3951  AOT_have proj2_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λxy [F]y]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
3952  AOT_have act_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]↓› for F by "cqt:2[lambda]"
3953  AOT_have act_beta: ‹❙⊢⇩□ [λz ❙𝒜[F]z]u ≡ ❙𝒜[F]u› for F u
3954    by (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E"]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
3955  AOT_modally_strict {
3956    fix x⇩1 x⇩2 y⇩1 y⇩2
3957    AOT_assume 0: ‹∀F ([F]x⇩1x⇩2 ≡ [F]y⇩1y⇩2)›
3958    AOT_have ‹[λxy [F]x]x⇩1x⇩2 ≡ [λxy [F]x]y⇩1y⇩2› for F
3959      by (rule 0[THEN "∀E"(1)]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
3960    AOT_have ‹ ❙⊢⇩□ ψ{[λμ⇩1...μ⇩n φ{μ⇩1...μ⇩n}]} ≡ ψ{[λxy φ{«(x,y)»}]}› for φ ψ
3961      by (simp add: "oth-class-taut:3:a")
3962    AOT_have xy1_eq: ‹([F]x⇩1 ≡ [F]y⇩1)› for F
3963      apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[F]x⇩1› ‹[λxy [F]x]x⇩1x⇩2›)
3964       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF proj1_den, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n,
3965                                 where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified, OF prod_den])
3966      apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[F]y⇩1› ‹[λxy [F]x]y⇩1y⇩2›)
3967       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF proj1_den, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n,
3968                                 where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified, OF prod_den])
3969      using "0" proj1_den "rule-ui:1" by blast
3970    AOT_hence ‹∀F([F]x⇩1 ≡ [F]y⇩1)› by (rule GEN)
3971    AOT_have xy2_eq: ‹([F]x⇩2 ≡ [F]y⇩2)› for F
3972      apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[F]x⇩2› ‹[λxy [F]y]x⇩1x⇩2›)
3973       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF proj2_den, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n,
3974                                 where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified, OF prod_den])
3975      apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹[F]y⇩2› ‹[λxy [F]y]y⇩1y⇩2›)
3976       apply (rule "beta-C-meta"[THEN "→E", OF proj2_den, unvarify ν⇩1ν⇩n,
3977                                 where τ=‹(_,_)›, simplified, OF prod_den])
3978      using "0" proj2_den "rule-ui:1" by blast
3979    AOT_hence ‹∀F([F]x⇩2 ≡ [F]y⇩2)› by (rule GEN)
3980
3981    AOT_have ‹(∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(x⇩2,F) & Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u))) →
3982              (∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y⇩2,F) & Numbers(y⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u)))›
3983    proof (rule "→I")
3984      AOT_assume ‹∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(x⇩2,F) & Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
3985      then AOT_obtain F where ‹∃u ([F]u & Numbers(x⇩2,F) & Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
3986        using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
3987      then AOT_obtain u where ‹[F]u & Numbers(x⇩2,F) & Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u)›
3988        using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by meson
3989      AOT_hence Fu: ‹[F]u›
3990            and numbers_x2_F: ‹Numbers(x⇩2,F)›
3991            and numbers_x1_F_minus_u: ‹Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u)›
3992        using "&E" by blast+
3993
3994      AOT_hence ‹[λx Numbers(x,F)]x⇩2›
3995        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) numbers_prop_den intro: "cqt:2")
3996      AOT_hence ‹[λx Numbers(x,F)]y⇩2›
3997        using xy2_eq[unvarify F, OF numbers_prop_den, THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
3998      AOT_hence numbers_y2_F: ‹Numbers(y⇩2,F)›
3999        by (rule "β→C"(1))
4000      AOT_have ‹[F]⇧-⇧u↓›
4001        using "≡⇩d⇩fE" "&E"(1) "&E"(2) numbers numbers_x1_F_minus_u by blast
4002      AOT_hence ‹[λx Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u)]x⇩1›
4003        by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) numbers_prop_den[unvarify G]
4004                  intro: "cqt:2" simp: numbers_x1_F_minus_u)
4005      AOT_hence ‹[λx Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u)]y⇩1›
4006        using xy1_eq[unvarify F, OF numbers_prop_den[unvarify G, OF "F-u[den]"],
4007                     THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
4008      AOT_hence numbers_y_1_F_minus_u: ‹Numbers(y⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u)›
4009        by (rule "β→C"(1))
4010
4011      AOT_show ‹∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y⇩2,F) & Numbers(y⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
4012        by (safe intro!: "∃I"(2)[where β=F] "Ordinary.∃I"[where β=u] "&I"
4013                         Fu numbers_y2_F numbers_y_1_F_minus_u)
4014    qed
4015  } note 0 = this
4016  AOT_modally_strict {
4017    fix x⇩1 x⇩2 y⇩1 y⇩2
4018    AOT_assume ‹∀F ([F]x⇩1x⇩2 ≡ [F]y⇩1y⇩2)›
4019    moreover AOT_have ‹∀F ([F]y⇩1y⇩2 ≡ [F]x⇩1x⇩2)›
4020      using calculation "cqt-basic:11" "≡E"(1) by fastforce
4021    ultimately AOT_have ‹∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(x⇩2,F) & Numbers(x⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u)) ≡
4022                         ∃F ∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y⇩2,F) & Numbers(y⇩1,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
4023      using 0 "≡I" "→E" by auto
4024  } note 0 = this
4025  AOT_show ‹[λxy ∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))]↓›
4026    apply (rule "kirchner-thm:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)]; rule RN)
4027    apply (rule tuple_forall[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
4028    apply (rule GEN)
4029    apply (rule GEN)
4030    apply (rule tuple_forall[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
4031    apply (rule GEN)
4032    apply (rule GEN)
4033    using 0 "→I" by simp
4034qed

4057AOT_theorem "pred-1-1:1": ‹[𝒫]xy → □[𝒫]xy›
4058proof(rule "→I")
4059  AOT_assume ‹[𝒫]xy›
4060  AOT_hence ‹∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
4061    using "≡E"(1) "pred-thm:3" by fast
4062  then AOT_obtain F where ‹∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
4063    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
4064  then AOT_obtain u where props: ‹[F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u)›
4065    using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] by meson
4066  AOT_obtain G where Ridigifies_G_F: ‹Rigidifies(G, F)›
4067    by (metis "instantiation" "rigid-der:3")
4068  AOT_hence ξ: ‹□∀x([G]x → □[G]x)› and ζ: ‹∀x([G]x ≡ [F]x)›
4069    using "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(1),
4070                           THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF "df-rigid-rel:1"], THEN "&E"(2)]
4071          "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2)] by blast+
4072
4073  AOT_have rigid_num_nec: ‹Numbers(x,F) & Rigidifies(G,F) → □Numbers(x,G)›
4074    for x G F
4075  proof(rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
4076    fix G F x
4077    AOT_assume Numbers_xF: ‹Numbers(x,F)›
4078    AOT_assume ‹Rigidifies(G,F)›
4079    AOT_hence ξ: ‹Rigid(G)› and ζ: ‹∀x([G]x ≡ [F]x)›
4080      using "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast+
4081    AOT_thus ‹□Numbers(x,G)›
4082    proof (safe intro!:
4083          "num-cont:2"[THEN "→E", OF ξ, THEN "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"],
4084                       THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"]
4085          "num-tran:3"[THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(1), rotated, OF Numbers_xF]
4086          eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]
4087            "&I" "cqt:2[const_var]"[axiom_inst] Ordinary.GEN "→I")
4088      AOT_show ‹[F]u ≡ [G]u› for u
4089        using ζ[THEN "∀E"(2)] by (metis "≡E"(6) "oth-class-taut:3:a") 
4090    qed
4091  qed
4092  AOT_have ‹□Numbers(y,G)›
4093    using rigid_num_nec[THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF props[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)],
4094                        OF Ridigifies_G_F].
4095  moreover {
4096    AOT_have ‹Rigidifies([G]⇧-⇧u, [F]⇧-⇧u)›
4097    proof (safe intro!: "df-rigid-rel:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "df-rigid-rel:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]
4098                        "&I" "F-u[den]" GEN "≡I" "→I")
4099      AOT_have ‹□∀x([G]x → □[G]x) → □∀x([[G]⇧-⇧u]x → □[[G]⇧-⇧u]x)›
4100      proof (rule RM; safe intro!: "→I" GEN)
4101        AOT_modally_strict {
4102          fix x
4103          AOT_assume 0: ‹∀x([G]x → □[G]x)›
4104          AOT_assume 1: ‹[[G]⇧-⇧u]x›

4106            apply (rule "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fE"(1), where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified])
4107             apply "cqt:2[lambda]"
4108            by (fact 1)
4109          AOT_hence ‹[G]x & x ≠⇩E u›
4110            by (rule "β→C"(1))
4111          AOT_hence 2: ‹□[G]x› and 3: ‹□x ≠⇩E u›
4112            using "&E" 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"] "id-nec4:1" "≡E"(1) by blast+
4113          AOT_show ‹□[[G]⇧-⇧u]x›

4136        by (auto intro: "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fI"(1), where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified]

4367      AOT_assume ‹∃v [[λx [O!]x & x =⇩E u]⇧-⇧u]v›
4368      then AOT_obtain v where ‹[[λx [O!]x & x =⇩E u]⇧-⇧u]v›
4369        using "Ordinary.∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
4370      AOT_hence ‹[λz [λx [O!]x & x =⇩E u]z & z ≠⇩E u]v›
4371        apply (rule "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fE"(1), where τ⇩1τ⇩n="(_,_)", simplified, rotated])
4372        by "cqt:2[lambda]"
4373      AOT_hence ‹[λx [O!]x & x =⇩E u]v & v ≠⇩E u›
4374        by (rule "β→C"(1))
4375      AOT_hence ‹v =⇩E u› and ‹v ≠⇩E u›
4376        using "β→C"(1) "&E" by blast+
4377      AOT_hence ‹v =⇩E u & ¬(v =⇩E u)›
4378        by (metis "≡E"(4) "reductio-aa:1" "thm-neg=E")
4379      AOT_thus ‹p & ¬p› for p
4380        by (metis "raa-cor:1")
4381    qed
4382  qed
4383  AOT_thus ‹∃z ([𝒫]0z & [𝒫]0z)›
4384    by (safe intro!: "&I" "∃I"(2)[where β=a])
4385qed

4387AOT_theorem "mod-col-num:1": ‹[ℕ]x → □[ℕ]x›
4388proof(rule "→I")
4389  AOT_have nec0N: ‹[λx □[ℕ]x]0›
4390    by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" simp: "zero:2" RN "0-n")
4391  AOT_have 1: ‹[λx □[ℕ]x]0 &
4392    ∀x∀y ([[𝒫]⇧+]0x & [[𝒫]⇧+]0y → ([𝒫]xy → ([λx □[ℕ]x]x → [λx □[ℕ]x]y))) →
4393    ∀x ([[𝒫]⇧+]0x → [λx □[ℕ]x]x)›
4394    by (auto intro!: "cqt:2"
4395              intro: "pre-ind"[unconstrain ℛ, unvarify β, OF "pred-thm:2",
4396                               THEN "→E", OF "pred-1-1:4", unvarify z, OF "zero:2",
4397                               unvarify F])
4398  AOT_have ‹∀x ([[𝒫]⇧+]0x → [λx □[ℕ]x]x)›
4399  proof (rule 1[THEN "→E"]; safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" nec0N;
4400         frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
4401    fix x y
4402    AOT_assume ‹[𝒫]xy›
4403    AOT_hence 0: ‹□[𝒫]xy›
4404      by (metis "pred-1-1:1" "→E")
4405    AOT_assume ‹[λx □[ℕ]x]x›
4406    AOT_hence ‹□[ℕ]x›
4407      by (rule "β→C"(1))
4408    AOT_hence ‹□([𝒫]xy & [ℕ]x)›
4409      by (metis "0" "KBasic:3" Adjunction "≡E"(2) "→E")
4410    moreover AOT_have ‹□([𝒫]xy & [ℕ]x) → □[ℕ]y›
4411    proof (rule RM; rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
4412      AOT_modally_strict {
4413        AOT_assume 0: ‹[𝒫]xy›
4414        AOT_assume ‹[ℕ]x›
4415        AOT_hence 1: ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0x›
4416          by (metis "≡E"(1) "nnumber:3")
4417        AOT_show ‹[ℕ]y›
4418          apply (rule "nnumber:3"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
4419          apply (rule "assume1:5"[unvarify x, OF "zero:2", THEN "≡E"(2)])
4420          apply (rule "∨I"(1))
4421          apply (rule "w-ances-her:3"[unconstrain ℛ, unvarify β, OF "pred-thm:2",
4422                                      THEN "→E", OF "pred-1-1:4", unvarify x,
4423                                      OF "zero:2", THEN "→E"])
4424          apply (rule "&I")
4425           apply (fact 1)
4426          by (fact 0)
4427      }
4428    qed
4429    ultimately AOT_have ‹□[ℕ]y›
4430      by (metis "→E") 
4431    AOT_thus ‹[λx □[ℕ]x]y›
4432      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
4433  qed
4434  AOT_hence 0: ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0x → [λx □[ℕ]x]x›
4435    using "∀E"(2) by blast
4436  AOT_assume ‹[ℕ]x›
4437  AOT_hence ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0x›
4438    by (metis "≡E"(1) "nnumber:3")
4439  AOT_hence ‹[λx □[ℕ]x]x›
4440    using 0[THEN "→E"] by blast
4441  AOT_thus ‹□[ℕ]x›
4442    by (rule "β→C"(1))
4443qed

4513    by (metis "≡E"(1) "nnumber:3" Number.ψ)
4514  AOT_show ‹[F]n›
4515    apply (rule "pre-ind"[unconstrain ℛ, unvarify β, THEN "→E", OF "pred-thm:2",
4516                          OF "pred-1-1:4", unvarify z, OF "zero:2", THEN "→E",
4517                          THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E"];
4518           safe intro!: 0 "&I" GEN "→I" F0)

4581proof (rule "→I")

4583  AOT_have ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0 n›
4584    using Number.ψ "≡E"(1) "nnumber:3" by blast
4585  AOT_hence ‹[[𝒫]⇧*]0 n ∨ 0 =⇩𝒫 n›
4586    using "assume1:5"[unvarify x, OF "zero:2"] by (metis "≡E"(1))
4587  moreover {

4589    AOT_hence ‹∃z ([𝒫]0z & [𝒫]nz)›
4590      using "assume1:2"[unvarify x, OF "zero:2", THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
4591    then AOT_obtain a where ‹[𝒫]0a & [𝒫]na› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
4592    AOT_hence ‹0 = n›

4597      using 0 "rule=E" id_sym by fast

4600    AOT_hence ‹∃x [𝒫]x 0 & ¬∃x [𝒫]x 0›
4601      by (metis "no-pred-0:1" "raa-cor:3")
4602  }

4606    using "w-ances-her:7"[unconstrain ℛ, unvarify β, OF "pred-thm:2",
4607                          THEN "→E", OF "pred-1-1:4", unvarify x,
4608                          OF "zero:2", THEN "→E"] by blast
4609  then AOT_obtain b where b_prop: ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0b & [𝒫]bn›
4610    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
4611  AOT_hence ‹[ℕ]b›
4612    by (metis "&E"(1) "≡E"(2) "nnumber:3")
4613  moreover AOT_have ‹x = b›
4614    using "pred-1-1:3"[THEN "df-1-1:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"], THEN "&E"(2),
4615                       THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E",
4616                       OF "&I", OF 0, OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]].
4617  ultimately AOT_show ‹[ℕ]x›
4618    using "rule=E" id_sym by fast
4619qed

4655AOT_theorem "pred-func:1": ‹[𝒫]xy & [𝒫]xz → y = z›
4656proof (rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2))
4657  AOT_assume ‹[𝒫]xy›
4658  AOT_hence ‹∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
4659    using "pred-thm:3"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
4660  then AOT_obtain F where ‹∃u ([F]u & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
4661    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
4662  then AOT_obtain a where
4663            Oa: ‹O!a›
4664    and a_prop: ‹[F]a & Numbers(y,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧a)›
4665    using "∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
4666  AOT_assume ‹[𝒫]xz›
4667  AOT_hence ‹∃F∃u ([F]u & Numbers(z,F) & Numbers(x,[F]⇧-⇧u))›
4668    using "pred-thm:3"[THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
4669  then AOT_obtain G where ‹∃u ([G]u & Numbers(z,G) & Numbers(x,[G]⇧-⇧u))›
4670    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
4671  then AOT_obtain b where Ob: ‹O!b›
4672                  and b_prop: ‹[G]b & Numbers(z,G) & Numbers(x,[G]⇧-⇧b)›
4673    using "∃E"[rotated] "&E" by blast
4674  AOT_have ‹[F]⇧-⇧a ≈⇩E  [G]⇧-⇧b›
4675    using "num-tran:2"[unvarify G H, OF "F-u[den]", OF "F-u[den]",
4676                       THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF a_prop[THEN "&E"(2)],
4677                       OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(2)]].
4678  AOT_hence ‹F ≈⇩E G›
4679    using "P'-eq"[unconstrain u, THEN "→E", OF Oa, unconstrain v, THEN "→E",
4680                  OF Ob, THEN "→E", OF "&I", OF "&I"]
4681          a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)]
4682          b_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(1)] by blast
4683  AOT_thus ‹y = z›
4684    using "pre-Hume"[THEN "→E", THEN "≡E"(2), OF "&I",
4685                     OF a_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)],
4686                     OF b_prop[THEN "&E"(1), THEN "&E"(2)]]
4687    by blast
4688qed

4704axiomatization ω_nat :: ‹ω ⇒ nat› where ω_nat: ‹surj ω_nat›
4705text‹Unfortunately, since the axiom requires the type @{typ ω}
4706     to have an infinite domain, @{command nitpick} can only find a potential model
4707     and no genuine model.
4708     However, since we could trivially choose @{typ ω} as a copy of @{typ nat},
4709     we can still be assured that above axiom is consistent.›
4710lemma ‹True› nitpick[satisfy, user_axioms, card nat=1, expect = potential] ..
4711
4712(* TODO: clean up a lot of noise in this proof *)
4713AOT_axiom "modal-axiom":
4714  ‹∃x([ℕ]x & x = #G) → ◇∃y([E!]y & ∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y))›
4715proof(rule AOT_model_axiomI)
4716  define urrel_act_ωext :: ‹urrel ⇒ ω set› where
4717    ‹urrel_act_ωext ≡ λ r . {x :: ω . AOT_model_valid_in w⇩0 (Rep_urrel r (ωυ x))}›
4718  define urrel_card_n :: ‹urrel ⇒ nat ⇒ bool› where
4719    ‹urrel_card_n ≡ λ r n . finite (urrel_act_ωext r) ∧
4720                             Finite_Set.card (urrel_act_ωext r) = n›
4721  define model_nat :: ‹<κ>› where

5069          ‹v = (THE v . [w⇩0 ⊨ [Π']«ωκ v»] ∧ [w⇩0 ⊨ [R]«ωκ a»«ωκ v»])›

5403                  AOT_sem_equiv κ.disc(7) "thm-neg=E") 
5404    next
5405      AOT_show ‹«ωκ x»↓›
5406        by (simp add: AOT_model_denotes_κ_def AOT_sem_denotes)
5407    qed
5408  } note 0 = this

5580        }

5582          using "KBasic:16" "&I" "→E" by fast

5584          using "RE◇" "≡E"(4) "Commutativity of &" "raa-cor:3" by blast

5593    } note 0 = this
5594    AOT_show ‹∃x([ℕ]x & x = #G) → ◇∃y([E!]y & ∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y))›

5602        by (rule "rule=E"[rotated, OF F_def])
5603      AOT_hence ‹∀G ([ℕ]x & [λx x = #G]x → ◇∃y([E!]y & ∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y)))›
5604        by (rule "β→C"(1))

5616AOT_theorem "modal-lemma":
5617  ‹◇∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v) → ∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v)›
5618proof(safe intro!: "→I" Ordinary.GEN)
5619  AOT_modally_strict {
5620    fix u
5621    AOT_assume act_Gu: ‹❙𝒜[G]u›
5622    AOT_have ‹∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v) → u ≠⇩E v›
5623    proof(rule "→I")
5624      AOT_assume ‹∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v)›
5625      AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v›
5626        using "Ordinary.∀E" by fast
5627      AOT_thus ‹u ≠⇩E v›
5628        using act_Gu "→E" by blast
5629    qed
5630  } note 0 = this
5631  AOT_have θ: ‹□(∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v) → u ≠⇩E v)› if ‹□❙𝒜[G]u› for u
5632  proof -
5633    AOT_have ‹□❙𝒜[G]u → □(∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v) → u ≠⇩E v)›
5634      apply (rule RM) using 0 "&E" "→I" by blast
5635    thus ?thesis using that "→E" by blast
5636  qed
5637  fix u
5638  AOT_assume 1: ‹◇∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v)›
5639  AOT_assume ‹❙𝒜[G]u›
5640  AOT_hence ‹□❙𝒜[G]u›
5641    by (metis "Act-Basic:6" "≡E"(1))
5642  AOT_hence ‹□(∀u (❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E v) → u ≠⇩E v)›
5643    using Ordinary.ψ θ by blast
5644  AOT_hence ‹◇u ≠⇩E v›
5645    using 1 "K◇"[THEN "→E", THEN "→E"] by blast
5646  AOT_thus ‹u ≠⇩E v›
5647    by (metis "id-nec4:2" "≡E"(1)) 
5648qed

5650AOT_theorem "th-succ": ‹∀n∃!m [𝒫]nm›
5651proof(safe intro!: Number.GEN "→I" "uniqueness:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
5652  fix n
5653  AOT_have ‹NaturalCardinal(n)›
5654    by (metis "nat-card" Number.ψ "→E")
5655  AOT_hence ‹∃G(n = #G)›
5656    by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" card)
5657  then AOT_obtain G where n_num_G: ‹n = #G›
5658    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5659  AOT_hence ‹∃n (n = #G)›
5660    by (rule "Number.∃I")
5661  AOT_hence ‹◇∃y ([E!]y & ∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y))›
5662    using "modal-axiom"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E"] by blast
5663  AOT_hence ‹∃y ◇([E!]y & ∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y))›
5664    using "BF◇"[THEN "→E"] by auto
5665  then AOT_obtain y where ‹◇([E!]y & ∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y))›
5666    using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5667  AOT_hence ‹◇E!y› and 2: ‹◇∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y)›
5668    using "KBasic2:3" "&E" "→E" by blast+
5669  AOT_hence Oy: ‹O!y›
5670    by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" intro: AOT_ordinary[THEN "=⇩d⇩fI"(2)])
5671  AOT_have 0: ‹∀u(❙𝒜[G]u → u ≠⇩E y)›
5672    using 2 "modal-lemma"[unconstrain v, THEN "→E", OF Oy, THEN "→E"] by simp
5673  AOT_have 1: ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]↓›
5674    by "cqt:2"
5675  AOT_obtain b where b_prop: ‹Numbers(b, [λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y])›
5676    using "num:1"[unvarify G, OF 1] "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5677  AOT_have Pnb: ‹[𝒫]nb›
5678  proof(safe intro!: "pred-thm:3"[THEN "≡E"(2)]
5679                     "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]»›]
5680                     1 "∃I"(2)[where β=y] "&I" Oy b_prop)
5681    AOT_show ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]y›
5682      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2" "∨I"(2)
5683                       "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF Oy])
5684  next
5685    AOT_have equinum: ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]⇧-⇧y ≈⇩E [λx ❙𝒜[G]x]›
5686    proof(rule "apE-eqE:1"[unvarify F G, THEN "→E"];
5687          ("cqt:2[lambda]" | rule "F-u[den]"[unvarify F]; "cqt:2[lambda]")?)
5688      AOT_show ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]⇧-⇧y ≡⇩E [λx ❙𝒜[G]x]›
5689      proof (safe intro!: eqE[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "F-u[den]"[unvarify F]
5690                          Ordinary.GEN "→I"; "cqt:2"?)
5691        fix u
5692        AOT_have ‹[[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ [(=⇩E)]xy]⇧-⇧y]u ≡ ([λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]u) & u ≠⇩E y›
5693          apply (rule "F-u"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)[where τ⇩1τ⇩n=‹(_,_)›], simplified]; "cqt:2"?)
5694          by (rule "beta-C-cor:2"[THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2)]; "cqt:2")
5695        also AOT_have ‹… ≡  (❙𝒜[G]u ∨ u =⇩E y) & u ≠⇩E y›
5696          apply (AOT_subst ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ [(=⇩E)]xy]u› ‹❙𝒜[G]u ∨ u =⇩E y›)
5697           apply (rule "beta-C-cor:2"[THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2)]; "cqt:2")
5698          using "oth-class-taut:3:a" by blast
5699        also AOT_have ‹… ≡ ❙𝒜[G]u›
5700        proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
5701          AOT_assume ‹(❙𝒜[G]u ∨ u =⇩E y) & u ≠⇩E y›
5702          AOT_thus ‹❙𝒜[G]u›
5703            by (metis "&E"(1) "&E"(2) "∨E"(3) "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E")
5704        next
5705          AOT_assume ‹❙𝒜[G]u›
5706          AOT_hence ‹u ≠⇩E y› and ‹❙𝒜[G]u ∨ u =⇩E y›
5707            using 0[THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", OF Ordinary.ψ, THEN "→E"]
5708                  "∨I" by blast+
5709          AOT_thus ‹(❙𝒜[G]u ∨ u =⇩E y) & u ≠⇩E y›
5710            using "&I" by simp
5711        qed
5712        also AOT_have ‹… ≡ [λx ❙𝒜[G]x]u›
5713          by (rule "beta-C-cor:2"[THEN "→E", THEN "∀E"(2), symmetric]; "cqt:2")
5714        finally AOT_show ‹[[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ [(=⇩E)]xy]⇧-⇧y]u ≡ [λx ❙𝒜[G]x]u›.
5715      qed
5716    qed
5717    AOT_have 2: ‹[λx ❙𝒜[G]x]↓› by "cqt:2[lambda]"
5718    AOT_show ‹Numbers(n,[λx ❙𝒜[G]x ∨ x =⇩E y]⇧-⇧y)›
5719      using "num-tran:1"[unvarify G H, OF 2, OF "F-u[den]"[unvarify F, OF 1],
5720                       THEN "→E", OF equinum, THEN "≡E"(2),
5721                       OF "eq-num:2"[THEN "≡E"(2), OF n_num_G]].
5722  qed
5723  AOT_show ‹∃α ([ℕ]α & [𝒫]nα & ∀β ([ℕ]β & [𝒫]nβ → β = α))›
5724  proof(safe intro!: "∃I"(2)[where β=b] "&I" Pnb "→I" GEN)
5725    AOT_show ‹[ℕ]b› using "suc-num:1"[THEN "→E", OF Pnb].
5726  next
5727    fix y
5728    AOT_assume 0: ‹[ℕ]y & [𝒫]ny›
5729    AOT_show ‹y = b›
5730      apply (rule "pred-func:1"[THEN "→E"])
5731      using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] Pnb "&I" by blast
5732  qed
5733qed

5752AOT_theorem "suc-fact": ‹n = m → n❙' = m❙'›
5753proof (rule "→I")
5754  AOT_assume 0: ‹n = m›
5755  AOT_show ‹n❙' = m❙'›
5756    apply (rule "rule=E"[rotated, OF 0])
5757    by (rule "=I"(1)[OF "def-suc[den2]"])
5758qed
5759
5760AOT_theorem "ind-gnd": ‹m = 0 ∨ ∃n(m = n❙')›
5761proof -
5762  AOT_have ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0m›
5763    using Number.ψ "≡E"(1) "nnumber:3" by blast
5764  AOT_hence ‹[[𝒫]⇧*]0m ∨ 0 =⇩𝒫 m›
5765    using "assume1:5"[unvarify x, OF "zero:2", THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
5766  moreover {
5767    AOT_assume ‹[[𝒫]⇧*]0m›
5768    AOT_hence ‹∃z ([[𝒫]⇧+]0z & [𝒫]zm)›
5769      using "w-ances-her:7"[unconstrain ℛ, unvarify β x, OF "zero:2",
5770                            OF "pred-thm:2", THEN "→E", OF "pred-1-1:4",
5771                            THEN "→E"]
5772      by blast
5773    then AOT_obtain z where θ: ‹[[𝒫]⇧+]0z› and ξ: ‹[𝒫]zm›
5774      using "&E" "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5775    AOT_have Nz: ‹[ℕ]z›
5776      using θ "≡E"(2) "nnumber:3" by blast
5777    moreover AOT_have ‹m = z❙'›
5778    proof (rule "def-suc"[THEN "=⇩d⇩fI"(1)];
5779           safe intro!: "def-suc[den1]"[unconstrain n, THEN "→E", OF Nz]
5780                        "nec-hintikka-scheme"[THEN "≡E"(2)] "&I"
5781                        GEN "→I" "Act-Basic:2"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
5782      AOT_show ‹❙𝒜[ℕ]m› using Number.ψ
5783        by (meson "mod-col-num:1" "nec-imp-act" "→E")
5784    next
5785      AOT_show ‹❙𝒜[𝒫]zm› using ξ
5786        by (meson "nec-imp-act" "pred-1-1:1" "→E")
5787    next
5788      fix y
5789      AOT_assume ‹❙𝒜([ℕ]y & [𝒫]zy)›
5790      AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[ℕ]y› and ‹❙𝒜[𝒫]zy›
5791        using "Act-Basic:2" "&E" "≡E"(1) by blast+
5792      AOT_hence 0: ‹[𝒫]zy›
5793        by (metis RN "≡E"(1) "pred-1-1:1" "sc-eq-fur:2" "→E")
5794      AOT_thus ‹y = m›
5795        using "pred-func:1"[THEN "→E", OF "&I"] ξ by metis
5796    qed
5797    ultimately AOT_have ‹[ℕ]z & m = z❙'›
5798      by (rule "&I")
5799    AOT_hence ‹∃n m = n❙'›
5800      by (rule "∃I")
5801    hence ?thesis
5802      by (rule "∨I")
5803  }
5804  moreover {
5805    AOT_assume ‹0 =⇩𝒫 m›
5806    AOT_hence ‹0 = m›
5807      using "id-R-thm:3"[unconstrain ℛ, unvarify β x, OF "zero:2", OF "pred-thm:2",
5808                         THEN "→E", OF "pred-1-1:4", THEN "→E"]
5809      by auto
5810    hence ?thesis using id_sym "∨I" by blast
5811  }
5812  ultimately show ?thesis
5813    by (metis "∨E"(2) "raa-cor:1")
5814qed
5815
5816AOT_theorem "suc-thm": ‹[𝒫]n n❙'›
5817proof -
5818  AOT_obtain x where m_is_n: ‹x = n❙'›
5819    using "free-thms:1"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF "def-suc[den2]"]
5820    using "∃E" by metis
5821  AOT_have ‹❙𝒜([ℕ]n❙' & [𝒫]n n❙')›
5822    apply (rule "rule=E"[rotated, OF suc_eq_desc[symmetric]])
5823    apply (rule "actual-desc:4"[THEN "→E"])
5824    by (simp add:  "def-suc[den1]")
5825  AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[ℕ]n❙'› and ‹❙𝒜[𝒫]n n❙'›
5826    using "Act-Basic:2" "≡E"(1) "&E" by blast+
5827  AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜[𝒫]nx›
5828    using m_is_n[symmetric] "rule=E" by fast+
5829  AOT_hence ‹[𝒫]nx›
5830    by (metis RN "≡E"(1) "pred-1-1:1" "sc-eq-fur:2" "→E")
5831  thus ?thesis
5832    using m_is_n "rule=E" by fast
5833qed

5847(* Note: we forgo restricted variables for natural cardinals. *)
5848AOT_define Finite :: ‹τ ⇒ φ› (‹Finite'(_')›)
5849  "inf-card:1": ‹Finite(x) ≡⇩d⇩f NaturalCardinal(x) & [ℕ]x›
5850AOT_define Infinite :: ‹τ ⇒ φ› (‹Infinite'(_')›)
5851  "inf-card:2": ‹Infinite(x) ≡⇩d⇩f NaturalCardinal(x) & ¬Finite(x)›
5852
5853AOT_theorem "inf-card-exist:1": ‹NaturalCardinal(#O!)›
5854  by (safe intro!: card[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "∃I"(1)[where τ=‹«O!»›] "=I"
5855                   "num-def:2"[unvarify G] "oa-exist:1")
5856
5857AOT_theorem "inf-card-exist:2": ‹Infinite(#O!)›
5858proof (safe intro!: "inf-card:2"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" "inf-card-exist:1")
5859  AOT_show ‹¬Finite(#O!)›
5860  proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
5861    AOT_assume ‹Finite(#O!)›
5862    AOT_hence 0: ‹[ℕ]#O!›
5863      using "inf-card:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E"(2) by blast
5864    AOT_have ‹Numbers(#O!, [λz ❙𝒜O!z])›
5865      using "eq-num:3"[unvarify G, OF "oa-exist:1"].
5866    AOT_hence ‹#O! = #O!›
5867      using "eq-num:2"[unvarify x G, THEN "≡E"(1), OF "oa-exist:1",
5868                       OF "num-def:2"[unvarify G], OF "oa-exist:1"]
5869      by blast
5870    AOT_hence ‹[ℕ]#O! & #O! = #O!›
5871      using 0 "&I" by blast
5872    AOT_hence ‹∃x ([ℕ]x & x = #O!)›
5873      using "num-def:2"[unvarify G, OF "oa-exist:1"] "∃I"(1) by fast
5874    AOT_hence ‹◇∃y ([E!]y & ∀u (❙𝒜[O!]u → u ≠⇩E y))›
5875      using "modal-axiom"[axiom_inst, unvarify G, THEN "→E", OF "oa-exist:1"] by blast
5876    AOT_hence ‹∃y ◇([E!]y & ∀u (❙𝒜[O!]u → u ≠⇩E y))›
5877      using "BF◇"[THEN "→E"] by blast
5878    then AOT_obtain b where ‹◇([E!]b & ∀u (❙𝒜[O!]u → u ≠⇩E b))›
5879      using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
5880    AOT_hence ‹◇[E!]b› and 2: ‹◇∀u (❙𝒜[O!]u → u ≠⇩E b)›
5881      using "KBasic2:3"[THEN "→E"] "&E" by blast+
5882    AOT_hence ‹[λx ◇[E!]x]b›
5883      by (auto intro!: "β←C"(1) "cqt:2")
5884    moreover AOT_have ‹O! = [λx ◇[E!]x]›
5885      by (rule "rule-id-df:1[zero]"[OF "oa:1"]) "cqt:2"
5886    ultimately AOT_have b_ord: ‹O!b›
5887      using "rule=E" id_sym by fast
5888    AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜O!b›
5889      by (meson "≡E"(1) "oa-facts:7")
5890    moreover AOT_have 2: ‹∀u (❙𝒜[O!]u → u ≠⇩E b)›
5891      using "modal-lemma"[unvarify G, unconstrain v, OF "oa-exist:1",
5892                          THEN "→E", OF b_ord, THEN "→E", OF 2].
5893    ultimately AOT_have ‹b ≠⇩E b›
5894      using "Ordinary.∀E"[OF 2, unconstrain α, THEN "→E",
5895                          OF b_ord, THEN "→E"] by blast
5896    AOT_hence ‹¬(b =⇩E b)›
5897      by (metis "≡E"(1) "thm-neg=E")
5898    moreover AOT_have ‹b =⇩E b›
5899      using "ord=Eequiv:1"[THEN "→E", OF b_ord].
5900    ultimately AOT_show ‹p & ¬p› for p
5901      by (metis "raa-cor:3")
5902  qed
5903qed
